0over%20and%20over%20again%20about%20the%20fact%20that%20you're%20using%20other%20people's%20money%20without%20their%20permission%2C%20I%20got%20bad%20news%20for%20SBF%2C%20that's%20fraud%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20impacts%20on%20the%20industry%20at%20large%2C%20Angel%20says%2C%20Bankman-Fried's%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Econviction%20comes%20amid%20a%20timely%20cleanup%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20certainly%20looks%20bad%20for%20Sam%2C%20no%20doubt%20about%20it%2C%20but%20I%20think%20it%20is%20a%20good%20cleansing%20for%20the%20crypto%20industry%2C%26quot%3B%20Angel%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20shows%20that%20the%20sheriff%20is%20riding%20into%20town%20and%20trying%20to%20clean%20up%20the%20mess.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20month-long%20trial%2C%20it%20took%20the%20jury%20four%20hours%20to%20convict%20Bankman-Fried%20on%20all%20seven%20counts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20sentencing%20hearing%20will%20be%20scheduled%20to%20decide%20how%20many%20years%20he%20spends%20in%20prison.%20If%20given%20the%20max%20on%20each%20count%2C%20it%20would%20be%20the%20rest%20of%20his%20natural%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sentencing%20schedule%20may%20depend%20on%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-bankman-fried-trial-all-criminal-charges-explained-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esecond%20criminal%20trial%3C%2Fa%3E%20Bankman-Fried%20faces%20for%20alleged%20illegal%20campaign%20contributions.%20That%20trial%20is%20scheduled%20for%20March%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-bankman-fried-implicated-friends-fraud-turned-on-him-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698970447000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65443ca73cc84b4dfafb7928%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-bankman-fried-implicated-f