%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65437ff33cc84b4dfafa9de3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-q4-earnings-tim-cook-comments-china-iphone-15-demand-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tim%20Cook%20tried%20to%20take%20a%20cheery%20note%20on%20iPhone%20demand%20in%20China%20during%20Apple's%20Q4%20earnings%2C%20but%20didn't%20say%20much%20about%20demand%20in%20the%20current%20quarter.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22gkay%40insider.com%20(Grace%20Kay)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A44%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-q4-earnings-tim-cook-comments-china-iphone-15-demand-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Charlie%20Javice's%20fraud%20trial%20prosecutors%20must%20press%20JP%20Morgan%20for%20more%20evidence%2C%20judge%20rules%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223237%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20is%20escorted%20into%20a%20courthouse.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F647f8c390821fb001810370e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222158%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECharlie%20Javice%20appeared%20in%20Federal%20Court%20in%20Manhattan%20on%20Nov.%202%2C%202023.%20%3Cp%3EMike%20Segar%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcharlie-javice-frank-jp-morgan-fraud-case-witholding-documents-slack-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECharlie%20Javice%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0appeared%20for%20a%20pretrial%20hearing%20Thursday%20in%20her%20fraud%20case.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Frank%20founder's%20lawyer%20accused%20federal%20prosecutors%20of%20withholding%20key%20evidence%20in%20the%20case.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20judge%20sided%20in%20part%20with%20the%20defense%2C%20ordering%20the%20government%20to%20force%20JP%20Morgan%20to%20release%20more%20evidence.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20federal%20judge%20on%20Thursday%20ruled%20that%20prosecutors%20must%20compel%20JP%20Morgan%20to%20find%20more%20evidence%20that%20could%20help%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcharlie-javice-frank-criminal-charges-financial-fraud-jpmorgan-chase-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECharlie%20Javice%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20financial%20aid%20startup%20Frank%2C%20in%20her%20defense%20in%20her%20criminal%20fraud%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20also%20set%20an%20October%202024%20start-date%20for%20the%20criminal%20trial%20of%20the%20embattled%20entrepreneur.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJavice%2C%2030%2C%20is%20accused%20of%20defrauding%20JP%20Morgan%20Chase%20out%20of%20%24175%20million%20in%202021%20by%20selling%20it%20a%20startup%20business%20called%20Frank%20which%20purported%20to%20help%20students%20navigate%20securing%20college%20loans.%20Federal%20prosecutors%20say%20that%20of%20the%20four%20million%20clients%20Javice%20claimed%20to%20have%2C%20only%20a%20few%20hundred%20thousand%20were%20legitimate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20inside%20U.S.%20Federal%20Court%20in%20Manhattan%2C%20lawyers%20for%20Javice%20and%20a%20co-defendant%20argued%20for%20more%20documents%20from%20JP%20Morgan%20Chase.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJavice's%20lawyer%2C%20Alex%20Spiro%2C%20argued%20that%20the%20government%20in%20its%20complaint%20had%20%26quot%3Bcherry%20picked%26quot%3B%20documents%20to%20make%20his%20client%20look%20culpable%2C%20but%20failed%20to%20adequately%20search%20for%20documents%20that%20might%20exonerate%20her.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGive%20us%20the%20one%20really%20bad%20email%20and%20don't%20give%20us%20something%20else%2C%26quot%3B%20Spiro%20said%20in%20court%2C%20describing%20the%20government's%20protocol.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20not%20how%20this%20case%20should%20proceed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAssistant%20U.S.%20Attorney%20Dina%20McLeod%20argued%20that%20the%20government%20was%20fair%20in%20sharing%20its%20evidence%20with%20the%20defense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20emails%2C%20if%20we%20have%20them%2C%20they%20have%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJudge%20Alvin%20K.%20Hellerstein%20ruled%20that%20in%20a%20handful%20of%20instances%20where%20specific%20emails%20were%20referenced%20in%20the%20complaint%2C%20the%20government%20needed%20to%20compel%20JP%20Morgan%20Chase%20to%20produce%20all%20emails%20in%20those%20chains%2C%20and%20all%20documents%20cited%20within.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20government%20is%20to%20require%20JP%20Morgan%20Chase%20to%20review%20its%20files%20and%20to%20assure%20that%20all%20parts%20of%20the%20chain%20in%20which%20these%20emails%20are%20a%20part%20have%20been%20provided%2C%20and%20all%20documents%20referenced%2C%26quot%3B%20Judge%20Hellerstein%20said%20from%20the%20bench.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%20the%20judge%20ruled%20against%20the%20defense's%20request%20that%20the%20government%20compel%20the%20financial%20behemoth%20to%20turn%20over%20additional%20emails%20from%20specific%20employees%20referenced%20in%20the%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpiro%20and%20a%20lawyer%20for%20Javice%20co-defendant%20Olivier%20Amar%2C%20Sean%20Buckley%2C%20said%20they%20soon%20would%20file%20a%20subpoena%20to%20get%20those%20additional%20emails%2C%20based%20on%20a%20different%20legal%20rule%20than%20the%20one%20they%20used%20to%20argue%20in%20court%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpiro%20repeated%20that%20he%20sought%2C%20%26quot%3Ball%20communications%20around%20all%20communications%26quot%3B%20that%20they%20saw%20fit%20to%20quote%20in%20their%20accusation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJudge%20Hellerstein%20warned%20that%20the%20defense's%20broad%20requests%20for%20documents%20was%20appropriate%20for%20a%20civil%20case%2C%20not%20a%20criminal%20one.%20He%20set%20a%20date%20for%20both%20sides%20to%20meet%20again%20in%20court%20on%20January%2017%2C%202024%20to%20work%20out%20further%20scheduling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20set%20October%2028%2C%202024%20as%20a%20trial%20start%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20a%20Delaware%20judge%20ruled%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcharlie-javice-jpmorgan-legal-bills-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJP%20Morgan%20Chase%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20violating%20a%20commitment%20that%20it%20made%20upon%20acquiring%20Frank%20to%20pay%20a%20significant%20portion%20of%20Javice's%20legal%20bills.%20Her%20lawyers%20say%20that%20JP%20Morgan%20Chase%20owes%20them%20%24835%2C000%20of%20the%20around%20%243.8%20million%20they%20have%20so%20far%20charged.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffrank-founder-charlie-javice-jp-morgan-fraud-trial-date-evidence-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698967426000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F652c0e6455f52b01b35fe1be%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffrank-founder-charlie-javice-jp-morgan-fraud-trial-date-evidence-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Charlie%20Javice's%20fraud%20trial%20start%20date%20is%20set.%20The%20judge%20also%20sided%20with%20the%20Frank%20founder's%20lawyers%2C%20ruling%20that%20JP%20Morgan%20must%20offer%20more%20evidence.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Nate%20Schweber)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffrank-founder-charlie-javice-jp-morgan-fraud-trial-date-evidence-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Apple%E2%80%99s%20sales%20drop%20slightly%20while%20profit%20is%20up%2011%25%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698967335000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104928188%2Cimgsize-34834.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Finternational-business%2Fapples-sales-drop-s