ok%20groups.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThese%20customers%20are%20high-intent%2C%20and%20it's%20often%20easier%20to%20build%20relationships%20with%20them.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EWhen%20using%20this%20approach%2C%20focus%20on%20providing%20value%20before%20promoting%20your%20business.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThis%20article%20is%20part%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarketing-for-small-business%5C%22%3EMarketing%20for%20Small%20Business%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20series%20exploring%20the%20basics%20of%20marketing%20strategy%20for%20SBOs%20to%20earn%20new%20customers%20and%20grow%20their%20business.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Danish%20Soomro%20started%20building%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvisadb.io%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVisadb.io%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20platform%20that%20helps%20people%20looking%20to%20move%20abroad%20hire%20visa%20and%20immigration%20experts%20%E2%80%94%20he%20struggled%20to%20find%20his%20target%20customers%20through%20standard%20digital%20marketing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20couldn't%20just%20run%20ads%20for%20it%20%E2%80%94%20I%20don't%20know%20when%20somebody's%20looking%20to%20move%2C%26quot%3B%20Soomro%20told%20Insider.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20knew%20that%20Facebook%20groups%20were%20a%20common%20place%20for%20people%20to%20ask%20questions%20and%20get%20recommendations%2C%20so%20he%20started%20joining%20groups%20for%20people%20looking%20to%20move%20to%20new%20countries%2C%20contributing%20to%20conversations%2C%20and%20sharing%20his%20product%20when%20it%20made%20sense.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20approach%20helped%20Soomro%20not%20only%20get%20in%20front%20of%20customers%20who%20were%20further%20along%20the%20funnel%20but%20also%20find%20suppliers%2C%20tech%20grants%2C%20and%20mentors%20through%20connections%20he%20made%20in%20the%20group.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20he%20found%20niche-community%20marketing%20so%20valuable%20that%20it%20inspired%20his%20next%20business%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fddevi.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDevi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20artificial-intelligence%20assistant%20that%20helps%20business%20owners%20monitor%20leads%20in%20Facebook%20groups%20and%20other%20social%20communities.%20Soomro%20grew%20Devi%20to%20a%20six-figure%20business%20in%2015%20months%20and%20grew%20his%20business%2022%25%20month%20over%20month%20from%20September%20to%20October%20by%20marketing%20primarily%20via%20private%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flauragatsosyoung.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELaura%20Gatsos%20Young%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20copywriting%20consultant%2C%20felt%20like%20she%20was%20screaming%20into%20a%20void%20when%20trying%20to%20find%20customers%20on%20more%20far-reaching%20marketing%20channels.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20the%20algorithms%2C%20you%20never%20know%20who's%20seeing%20what%2C%20and%20you%20don't%20know%20if%20you're%20actually%20interacting%20with%20someone%20who%20could%20potentially%20be%20a%20peer%2C%20a%20collaborator%2C%20a%20client%2C%20because%20you%20don't%20have%20that%20personal%20connection%20with%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Gatsos%20Young%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20past%20five%20years%2C%20she%20has%20focused%20her%20marketing%20on%20networking%20in%20private%20communities%2C%20where%20she%20has%20found%20clients%2C%20referrers%2C%20and%20collaboration%20opportunities%20such%20as%20guest%20teaching%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-podcast-interviews-can-support-your-brand-small-business-2023-10%5C%22%3Epodcast%20interviews%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20LinkedIn%20Lives.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInsider%20talked%20to%20Soomro%20and%20Gatsos%20Young%20for%20advice%20on%20how%20other%20small-business%20owners%20could%20successfully%20market%20in%20smaller%20online%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EFocus%20on%20quality%20of%20members%20over%20quantity%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESoomro's%20first%20piece%20of%20advice%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20not%20in%20the%20right%20groups%2C%20this%20tactic%20doesn't%20work.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20right%20groups%2C%20he%20added%2C%20don't%20necessarily%20mean%20the%20biggest%20ones.%20Instead%2C%20Soomro%20recommends%20seeking%20out%20communities%20where%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20members%20are%20your%20target%20audience.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22660%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Photo%20displaying%20an%20example%20of%20how%20private%20group%20promotion%20works.%20In%20the%20top%20post%2C%20a%20contributor%20asks%3A%20%26quot%3BLooking%20for%20lead%20gen%20for%20our%20saas%20company.%20What%20systems%20work%20in%20your%20opinion%3F%26quot%3B%20In%20his%20response%2C%20Soomro%20promotes%20his%20product.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6541626a36d588dc55c746d9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22679%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20example%20of%20a%20conversation%20where%20Soomro%20can%20promote%20his%20product.%3Cp%3EDanish%20Soomro%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%20this%20is%20very%20straightforward%20%E2%80%94%20for%20instance%2C%20when%20marketing%20Devi%2C%20Soomro%20joined%20several%20entrepreneurship%20groups%2C%20since%20those%20include%20his%20target%20audience.%20He%20also%20looked%20for%20groups%20tangentially%20related%20to%20his%20products.%20For%20Visadb%2C%20he%20found%20success%20in%20digital-nomad%20communities%2C%20since%20moving%20internationally%20is%20often%20part%20of%20the%20lifestyle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20in%20a%20huge%20community%2C%20you%20might%20not%20even%20get%20noticed%2C%26quot%3B%20Gatsos%20Young%20said.%20But%20if%20you're%20active%20in%20smaller%20communities%2C%20you%20can%20position%20yourself%20as%20the%20go-to%20person%20for%20your%20area%20of%20expertise.%20She%20also%20prefers%20paid%20communities%20%E2%80%94%20including%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdrmichellemazur.com%2Fexpert-up%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Expert%20Up%20Club%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbetheupside.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Upside%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20because%20the%20members%20are%20often%20more%20vetted%20and%20engaged%20than%20those%20in%20a%20free%20network.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20find%20the%20right%20groups%2C%20Soomro%20said%2C%20you%20can%20search%20Facebook%20by%20keyword%20or%20look%20online%20for%20top%20groups%20for%20your%20audience%20segment%20(e.g.%2C%20%26quot%3Btop%20groups%20for%20female%20entrepreneurs%26quot%3B).%20Gatsos%20Young%20also%20asks%20her%20clients%20which%20communities%20they're%20a%20part%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ELook%20for%20people%20asking%20for%20what%20you%20offer%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20thing%20you%20want%20to%20do%20once%20you%20join%20a%20group%2C%20Soomro%20said%2C%20is%20start%20publishing%20random%20posts%20promoting%20your%20product.%20For%20one%2C%20this%20may%20be%20against%20the%20guidelines%20of%20the%20community.%20But%20it%20will%20likely%20also%20come%20across%20as%20spammy%20and%20is%20less%20likely%20to%20be%20effective.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20he%20monitors%20the%20groups%20he's%20in%20to%20look%20for%20conversations%20where%20it%20makes%20sense%20to%20insert%20expertise%20related%20to%20his%20brand%20or%20plug%20his%20product.%20For%20instance%2C%20if%20someone%20asks%20for%20recommendations%20on%20lead-generation%20software%2C%20Soomro%20feels%20he%20adds%20value%20by%20sharing%20information%20about%20Devi%2C%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20do%20this%20by%20regularly%20scrolling%20through%20group%20posts%20and%20looking%20for%20conversations%20related%20to%20your%20work%2C%20or%20using%20the%20search%20function%20within%20groups%20to%20look%20for%20relevant%20keywords.%20Soomro%20used%20to%20have%20his%20virtual%20assistant%20monitor%20groups%20and%20identify%20opportunities%20to%20do%20outreach.%20Now%20he%20uses%20his%20own%20tool%2C%20Devi%2C%20to%20automatically%20track%20keywords%20and%20flag%20relevant%20conversations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20approach%20may%20be%20a%20big%20time%20investment%2C%20but%20participating%20in%20one%20conversation%20can%20easily%20lead%20to%20more%20than%20one%20lead%2C%20Soomro%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20person%20will%20get%20my%20product%2C%20but%20also%20other%20people%20in%20that%20group%20will%20learn%20about%20my%20services%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20When%20searching%20for%20test%20users%20for%20Devi%2C%20Soomro%20said%20that%2064%20comments%20in%20a%20Facebook%20group%20about%20his%20product%20led%20to%20600%20leads.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBe%20helpful%20instead%20of%20promotional%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESoomro's%20rule%20of%20thumb%20when%20engaging%20in%20any%20group%20is%20to%20offer%20more%20value%20than%20he's%20taking.%20Most%20of%20his%20comments%20involve%20more%20of%20a%20soft%20pitch%2C%20offering%20general%20advice%20about%20the%20question%20being%20asked%20and%20then%20gently%20pushing%20his%20products%20at%20the%20end%20when%20it%20makes%20sense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGatsos%20Young%20treads%20lighter%2C%20rarely%20selling%20herself%20directly.%20Instead%2C%20she%20focuses%20on%20providing%20value%20and%20building%20relationships%20in%20the%20groups%2C%20such%20as%20by%20hopping%20on%20quick%20calls%20with%20members%20who%20are%20struggling%20with%20a%20copywriting%20task.%20%26quot%3BJust%20by%20showing%20up%20and%20giving%20my%20advice%2C%20it's%20led%20to%20me%20either%20working%20with%20them%20later%20on%20down%20the%20line%20or%20them%20referring%20me%20to%20someone%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESales%20is%20an%20inherent%20benefit%20of%20being%20part%20of%20these%20communities%2C%20but%20you%20shouldn't%20approach%20them%20with%20the%20intention%20of%20getting%20business%2C%20Gatsos%20Young%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECustomers%20are%20diligent%20and%20discerning%20about%20whom%20they%20work%20with%2C%20she%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20show%20up%20in%20a%20community%20and%20you%20show%20up%20without%20expectation%20other%20than%20to%20have%20a%20meaningful%20conversation%2C%20I%20think%20it's%20a%20refresher%20for%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-small-businesses-use-online-communities-connect-customers-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698956265000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6541415336d588dc55c70e09%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-small-businesses-use-online-communities-connect-customers-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Private%20communities%2C%20such%20as%20Facebook%20groups%2C%20can%20offer%20a%20unique%20way%20for%20small-business%20owners%20to%20connect%20with%20customers%20authentically.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Erin%20Greenawald)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A63%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-small-businesses-use-online-communities-connect-customers-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dow%20soars%20564%20points%20as%20plummeting%20bond%20yields%20spark%20huge%20rally%20in%20US%20stocks%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Traders%20work%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20New%20York%20Stock%20Exchange%20(NYSE)%20on%20March%2028%2C%202023%20in%20New%20York%20City.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6532ccaf96f7540cd0620664%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETraders%20work%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20New%20York%20Stock%20