nder%20Indian%20democracy%2C%20eventually%20to%20destroy%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20Yechury%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBarring%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20is%20still%20undecided%20on%20whether%20to%20treat%20AAP%20as%20an%20ally%20or%20its%20rival%2C%20most%20other%20INDIA%20constituents%20have%20protested%20against%20the%20ED%20move%20to%20summon%20a%20sitting%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGiven%20how%20a%20majority%20of%20INDIA%20parties%20have%20reflexively%20raised%20the%20pitch%20against%20BJP%20on%20alleged%20misuse%20of%20central%20investigation%20agencies%20over%20the%20last%20few%20months%2C%20the%20issue%20is%20likely%20to%20remain%20a%20burning%20matter%20of%20discussion%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698937384000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F10%2F27145705%2FScreenshot-2022-10-27-at-2.56.15-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fed-summons-to-kejriwal-a-ploy-to-destroy-india-bloc-ahead-of-2024-lok-sabha-polls-aap%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22AAP%20alleged%20that%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20was%20being%20used%20by%20the%20BJP%20to%20finish%20off%20opposition%20forces%20who%20had%20come%20together%20to%20form%20the%20INDIA%20bloc.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fed-summons-to-kejriwal-a-ploy-to-destroy-india-bloc-ahead-of-2024-lok-sabha-polls-aap%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Boman%3A%20Audiences%20will%20enjoy%20my%20role%20in%20Dunki%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698937220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104922523%2Cimgsize-19976.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fdunki-actor-boman-irani-my-character-has-an-interesting-arc-that-im-hopeful-au