ax-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02171649%2F1e69c4de-fdc3-4862-aa3f-180c7f75ffcc.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02171649%2F1e69c4de-fdc3-4862-aa3f-180c7f75ffcc.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02171649%2F1e69c4de-fdc3-4862-aa3f-180c7f75ffcc-300x163.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02171649%2F1e69c4de-fdc3-4862-aa3f-180c7f75ffcc-1024x556.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-683196%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22652%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESarpanch%20Balbir%20Kaur%20interacting%20with%20locals%20after%20the%20recent%20ceasefire%20violation%20which%20damaged%20five%20residential%20homes%20in%20Trewa%20village.%20Photo%3A%20By%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reports%2C%20locals%20in%20Arnia%20have%20already%20started%20preparations%20for%20more%20difficult%20times%20amid%20the%20ongoing%20political%20uncertainty%20across%20the%20border%20following%20the%20ouster%20of%20Imran%20Khan%20as%20prime%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20unprovoked%20firing%20last%20week%2C%20residents%20of%20Trewa%20and%20adjoining%20villages%20in%20Arnia%20and%20RS%20Pura%20have%20cleaned%20up%20dozens%20of%20underground%20bunkers%20built%20by%20the%20government%2C%20where%20they%20take%20refuge%20when%20the%20situation%20heats%20up%20between%20the%20two%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20district%20administration%20in%20Jammu%20has%20also%20banned%20the%20sale%20and%20use%20of%20firecrackers%20during%20marriage%20ceremonies%20and%20other%20celebrations%20to%20prevent%20any%20confusion%20or%20rumour-mongering%20amid%20the%20simmering%20border%20tensions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPakistan%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20trusted.%20If%20they%20do%20it%20(mortar%20shelling)%20once%2C%20they%20will%20do%20it%20again.%20For%20me%2C%20the%20immediate%20priority%20is%20to%20help%20the%20farmers%20in%20harvesting%20their%20crops.%20Besides%2C%20we%20are%20also%20holding%20regular%20meetings%20with%20the%20residents%20so%20that%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20feel%20ignored%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Kaur%2C%20who%20is%20also%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Kisan%20Advisory%20Board.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20a%20patrol%20party%20of%20Border%20Security%20Forces%20detected%20and%20defused%20an%20unexploded%20mortar%20shell%20which%20was%20fired%20by%20Pakistan%20Rangers%20on%20October%2026.%20The%20BSF%20has%20already%20lodged%20a%20protest%20with%20Pakistan%20Rangers%20over%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20farms%20and%20houses%20are%20not%20safe%20unless%20there%20is%20a%20flag%20meeting%20between%20the%20armies%20(of%20India%20and%20Pakistan).%20Once%20it%20happens%2C%20there%20will%20be%20some%20hope%20that%20the%20situation%20will%20calm%20down%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20local%20who%20did%20not%20want%20to%20be%20named%20over%20the%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20situation%20has%20calmed%20down%20and%20no%20fresh%20incident%20of%20firing%20was%20reported%20after%20last%20week%E2%80%99s%20ceasefire%20violation%2C%20residents%20are%20not%20leaving%20anything%20up%20to%20fate.%20%E2%80%9CAn%20evacuation%20plan%20has%20been%20prepared.%20In%2030%20minutes%2C%20all%20the%20residents%20will%20be%20in%20underground%20bunkers%20if%20something%20ugly%20happens%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kaur%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20Pakistan%20used%20mortar%20shells%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20two%20years%2C%20authorities%20have%20put%20the%20BSF%20on%20a%20high%20alert%20along%20the%20International%20Border%20in%20Jammu.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20BSF%20continues%20to%20monitor%20the%20developments%20closely%2C%20while%20assessing%20the%20situation%20and%20remains%20alert%20to%20respond%20as%20necessary%20to%20ensure%20the%20safety%20and%20security%20of%20the%20border%20and%20its%20residents%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20BSF%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20shares%20a%203%2C323-km%20border%20with%20Pakistan%2C%20including%20965%20km%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20While%20221%20km%20is%20the%20demarcated%20International%20Border%2C%20744%20km%20is%20the%20Line%20of%20Control%20which%20came%20up%20as%20a%20result%20of%20hostilities%20between%20the%20two%20South%20Asian%20neighbours%20after%20the%201947%20partition.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20sanctioned%20the%20construction%20of%2018%2C460%20individual%20and%20community%20bunkers%20in%20five%20districts%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20%E2%80%93%20Jammu%2C%20Kathua%2C%20Samba%2C%20Poonch%2C%20and%20Rajouri%20which%20fall%20along%20the%20Line%20of%20Control%20and%20International%20Border%20to%20shield%20border%20residents%20from%20Pakistani%20shelling.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698928167000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02171714%2F6b5c8022-678b-4bd2-8840-7f28d05e4095.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpakistan-violates-ceasefire-residents-border-villages-fear-uncertainty%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20shelling%20has%20revived%20the%20fears%20of%20an%20escalation%20in%20violence%20along%20the%20International%20Border%20in%20the%20coming%20days.%20Locals%20said%20that%20farmers%20are%20afraid%20of%20venturing%20into%20their%20paddy%20fields%20to%20harvest%20their%20crops%2C%20putting%20their%20livelihood%20at%20risk.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpakistan-violates-ceasefire-residents-border-villages-fear-uncertainty%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Can%20the%20Modi%20Government%E2%80%99s%20