20the%20Modi%20government%20and%20the%20factors%20that%20play%20a%20role%20in%20contributing%20to%20developmental%20prospects.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EPradhan%20Mantri%20Kisan%20Samman%20Nidhi%20(PM-KISAN)%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPM-KISAN%20Yojana%20aims%20to%20supplement%20the%20financial%20needs%20of%20the%20farmers%20in%20acquiring%20various%20inputs%20to%20ensure%20proper%20crop%20health%20and%20appropriate%20yields%20and%20generate%20equivalent%20expected%20income%20for%20the%20farmers.%20This%20nationwide%20scheme%20was%20announced%20in%20the%202019%20interim%20budget%20of%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20small%20and%20marginal%20farmers%20would%20receive%20Rs%206%2C000%20per%20year%20in%20three%20payments%2C%20which%20will%20be%20put%20directly%20into%20their%20bank%20accounts%20under%20this%20initiative.%20The%20Union%20government%20would%20fund%20the%20total%20yearly%20expenditure%20for%20this%20initiative.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20programme%E2%80%99s%20benefits%20are%20now%20available%20to%20all%20farmers%20nationwide%20without%20the%20need%20for%20intermediaries%20through%20a%20farmer-centric%20digital%20infrastructure%20that%20upholds%20complete%20transparency%20in%20beneficiary%20verification%20and%20registration.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20of%20August%202023%2C%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20has%20disbursed%20over%20Rs%202.60%20lakhs%20crores%20to%20more%20than%2011%20crore%20farmers.%20In%20the%20last%20financial%20year%20i.e.%202022-23%2C%20a%20total%20amount%20of%20Rs%2058%2C201.85%20crore%20was%20disbursed%20to%20eligible%20beneficiaries.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F