%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20above%20graph%20demonstrates%20conclusively%20that%20the%20government%20has%20consistently%20underutilised%20the%20allocated%20funds%20for%20the%20programme.%20Except%20for%202021%2C%20the%20government%20consistently%20underutilised%20the%20allocated%20funds.%20A%20budget%20overrun%20in%202021%20was%20primarily%20attributable%20to%20the%20necessity%20of%20meeting%20the%20requirements%20of%20farmers%20during%20the%20second%20wave%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02160050%2Fimage3-1.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22901%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02160050%2Fimage3-1.png%20901w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02160050%2Fimage3-1-300x188.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-683177%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22564%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPercentage%20Budget%20Under-Utilisation.%20Source%3A%20Infosphere%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20above%20chart%20shows%20that%20the%20government%20made%20efforts%20to%20address%20the%20issue%20of%20underutilisation%20but%20still%20confronts%20an%20average%20rate%20of%2024%25%20of%20the%20budgeted%20amount.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EFactors%20shaping%20rural%20development%20patterns%20across%20India%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EFirstly%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20literacy%20rate%20trends%20have%20a%20major%20impact%20on%20rural%20development%20scenarios.%20A%20higher%20literacy%20rate%2C%20especially%20amongst%20girls%20in%20rural%20areas%2C%20has%20been%20responsible%20for%20the%20improved%20performance%20of%20many%20public%20health%20statistics%20and%20over%20time%20helped%20rural%20youth%20get%20absorbed%20in%20higher-paying%2C%20and%20better-condition%20employment%20opportunities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmospi.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fpublication_reports%2FReport_585_75th_round_Education_final_1507_0.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ENSS%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cspan%3Ereports%2C%20the%20literacy%20rate%20in%20rural%20India%20increased%20from%2068%25%20for%20males%20and%2043%25%20for%20females%20in%202000%20to%2072.3%25%20for%20males%20and%2056.8%25%20for%20females%20in%202014.%20Between%202003%20and%202014%2C%20rural%20literacy%20grew%20at%20a%20compound%20annual%20growth%20rate%20(CAGR)%20of%20approximately%203.42%25.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ibef.org%2Fblogs%2Frural-education-integral-to-india-s-progress%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E2021%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%3Cspan%3E%20the%20literacy%20rate%20stood%20at%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Earound%2073.5%25%20in%20rural%20India%2C%20including%2081%25%20for%20males%20and%2065%25%20for%20females.%20The%20government%20of%20India%20has%20launched%20many%20initiatives%20such%20as%20Samagra%20Shiksha%2C%20Jahawar%20Navodaya%20Vidyalaya%2C%20mid-day%20meal%20schemes%2C%20etc.%20to%20increase%20the%20enrolment%20rate%20and%20also%20to%20encourage%20the%20already%20enrolled%20students%20to%20attend%20regularly%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20rise%20in%20literacy%20rates.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStill%2C%20rural%20India%20requires%20a%20strong%20infrastructure%2C%20including%20roads%2C%20communication%20channels%2C%20electricity%2C%20drinking%20water%2C%20irrigation%2C%20drainage%2C%20and%20adequate%20housing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcensusindia.gov.in%2Fcensus.website%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ECensus%202011%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%2045%25%20of%20rural%20households%20do%20not%20have%20electricity%20connections%20and%20depend%20on%20kerosene%20and%20other%20means%20for%20lighting%20and%20merely%2030%25%20of%20rural%20areas%20are%20covered%20with%20tap%20water%20supply.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20addition%2C%20the%20sanitation%20facilities%20in%20rural%20areas%20are%20also%20not%20adequate.%20As%20per%20the%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmorth.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FBasic_Road_Statistics_of_India_2012_13_0.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eroad%20statistics%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20published%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20for%202012-13%2C%20rural%20roads%20span%2060.39%20km%20of%20every%20100%20km.%20Further%2C%20the%20rural%20surfaced%20road%20is%20just%2033%25%20of%20the%20total%20rural%20road%20network%20in%20India%20and%20the%20remaining%20are%20kutcha%20roads%20which%20are%20highly%20vulnerable%20and%20inaccessible%2C%20particularly%20during%20the%20rainy%20season.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVarious%20schemes%20and%20initiatives%20are%20being%20undertaken%20by%20the%20current%20government%20including%20the%20Jal%20Jeevan%20Mission%20which%20aims%20to%20provide%20functional%20household%20tap%20connection%20to%20every%20rural%20household%20by%202024.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20As%20of%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.investindia.gov.in%2Fteam-india-blogs%2Frural-infrastructure-sector-under-national-infrastructure-pipeline%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EDecember%2031%2C%202019%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20road%20length%20worth%20Rs.%202.9%20lakh%20crore%20had%20been%20sanctioned%20and%20expenditure%20of%20Rs.%202.17%20lakh%20crore%20was%20incurred.%20The%20vision%20for%202025%20is%20for%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.investindia.gov.in%2Fteam-india-blogs%2Frural-infrastructure-sector-under-national-infrastructure-pipeline%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E100%25%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20the%20rural%20population%20to%20have%20access%20to%20pucca%20houses%20with%20basic%20civic%20amenities%20such%20as%20piped%20drinking%20water%2C%20power%20supply%20and%20LPG%20connections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGovernment%20policies%20have%20helped%20to%20develop%20rural%20India%2C%20creating%20new%20job%20opportunities.%20One%20such%20initiative%20is%20TRYSEM%2C%20or%20Training%20Rural%20Youth%20for%20Self-Employment.%20It%20aims%20to%20train%20young%20people%20in%20technical%20skills%20so%20that%20they%20can%20start%20their%20businesses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMulti-pronged%20strategies%20are%20being%20taken%20by%20the%20Government%20to%20address%20issues%20relating%20to%20employment%20opportunities%20through%20centrally%20sponsored%20schemes%20like%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fharyanarural.gov.in%2Fmahatma-gandhi-national-rural-employment-guarantee-scheme-mgnregs%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520Government%2520of%2520India%2520passed%2Cto%2520do%2520unskilled%2520manual%2520work.%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMGNREGS%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.myscheme.gov.in%2Fschemes%2Fday-nrlm%23%3A~%3Atext%3DDeendayal%2520Antyodaya%2520Yojana%2520%252D%2520National%2520Rural%2520Livelihoods%2520Mission%2520(DAY%252DNRLM%2Ca%2520range%2520of%2520financial%2520services%5C%22%3E%20%3Cspan%3EDeendayal%20Antyoday%20Yojana-%20National%20Rural%20Livelihood%20Mission%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frural.nic.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FRTI_DDUGKY_05112021.pdf%5C%22%3E%20%3Cspan%3EDeendayal%20Upadhyay-%20Gramin%20Kaushalya%20Yojana%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fomms.nic.in%2F%5C%22%3E%20%3Cspan%3EPradhan%20Mantri%20Gram%20Sadak%20Yojana%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%20launched%20the%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1796217%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EGarib%20Kalyan%20Rojgar%20Abhiyaan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cspan%3E(GKRA)%20of%20125%20days%20on%20June%2020%2C%202020%20to%20boost%20employment%20and%20livelihood%20opportunities%20for%20returnee%20migrant%20workers%20and%20similarly%20affected%20persons%20including%20youth%20in%20rural%20areas%2C%20in%20116%20selected%20districts%20across%20Bihar%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Odisha%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20The%20Abhiyaan%20has%20achieved%20an%20employment%20generation%20of%2050.78%20crore%20person-days%20with%20a%20total%20expenditure%20of%20Rs%2039%2C293%20crore.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20rise%20of%20mass%20media%2C%20such%20as%20television%2C%20social%20media%2C%20and%20radio%2C%20has%20increased%20awareness%20among%20rural%20people.%20With%20mobile%20phones%20and%20the%20Internet%2C%20they%20can%20now%20search%20for%20jobs%2C%20learn%20new%20skills%2C%20and%20connect%20with%20people%20outside%20of%20their%20village.%20This%20has%20also%20made%20them%20more%20aware%20of%20different%20government%20schemes%20that%20can%20help%20them%20with%20farming%20and%20other%20activities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ficar.org.in%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIndian%20Council%20of%20Agricultural%20Research%20(ICAR)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20%3Cspan%3Eis%20responsible%20for%20agricultural%20research%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20helps%20understand%20how%20crop%20yields%20are%20affected%20by%20different%20atmospheric%20and%20soil%20conditions%2C%20and%20how%20fertilizers%20can%20be%20used%20to%20increase%20production%20leading%20to%20the%20overall%20development%20of%20the%20rural%20areas.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrom%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ficar.org.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2023-07%2FSignificant%2520Achievements%2520During%25202014-23%2520English%252017%2520July%252023.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E2014%20to%202023%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%3Cspan%3E%20ICAR%20has%20been%20able%20to%20release%202%2C764%20varieties%20of%20field%20and%20horticultural%20crops%20including%20123%20bio-fortified%20varieties.%20It%20has%20enhanced%20export-oriented%20production%20of%20horticultural%20crops%20and%20gene%20modifications%20to%20explore%20improved%20resistance%20to%20biotic%2Fabiotic%20stresses.%20ICAR%20was%20able%20to%20develop%2028%20eco-friendly%20pest%20management%20modules%20and.%2053%20multi-enterprise%20integrated%20farming%20systems%20(IFS).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EIn%20summation%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20root%20is%20still%20habituated%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20its%20villages%20even%20though%2C%20paradoxically%2C%20its%20cities%20power%20the%20growth%20story.%20The%20appropriation%20of%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Feconomy%2Findicators%2Fbright-spot-rural-consumption-to-pick-up-on-wage-rise-and-lower-inflation-say-economists%2Farticleshow%2F101647375.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Erural%20populations%E2%80%99%20hard%20work%20has%20become%20a%20cost-benefit%20advantage%20for%20urban%20areas%20to%20source%20cheap%20migrant%20worker%20bases%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20One%20can%20see%20that%20while%20analysing%20the%20growth%20of%20construction%2C%20or%20MSMEs%20too.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUpon%20assuming%20office%20in%202014%2C%20the%20Modi%20administration%20instilled%20considerable%20optimism%20on%20the%20prospects%20of%20rural%20reform%20and%20the%20lofty%20objective%20of%20doubling%20the%20earnings%20of%20farmers.%20Nevertheless%2C%20in%202019%2C%20the%20development%20achieved%20was%20not%20in%20line%20with%20the%20initial%20expectations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20a%20considerable%20segment%20of%20the%20rural%20voting%20population%20maintained%20a%20sense%20of%20optimism%20and%20adopted%20a%20cautious%20stance%2C%20expecting%20that%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20subsequent%20term%20in%20office%20would%20yield%20the%20desired%20transformations%20they%20longed%20for.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F05%2F26171336%2Fdap.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F05%2F26171336%2Fdap.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F05%2F26171336%2Fdap-300x150.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F05%2F26171336%2Fdap-1024x513.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F05%2F26171336%2Fdap-800x400.jpg%20800w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-530667%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22601%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERepresentative%20image%20of%20a%20farmer%20spraying%20fertilizer.%20Photo%3A%20IFPRI%2FFlickr%20CC%20BY%20NC%20ND%202.0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERoad%20construction%20and%20better%20connectivity%20have%20helped%20remote%20areas%20to%20be%20better%20connected%20than%20before%20but%20rural%20livelihoods%2C%20and%20access%20to%20basic%20amenities%2C%20including%20better%20education%2C%20healthcare%2C%20or%20employment%2C%20remain%20a%20distant%20goal.%20This%20has%20negatively%20impacted%20the%20upward%20mobility%20promise%20that%20(new)%20governments%20bring%20with%20them%20when%20they%20expect%20to%20be%20voted%20back%20to%20power.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EProgrammes%20like%20MGNREGS%20have%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frural.nic.in%2F