MK.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHyderabad%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(BRS)%20chief%20K.%20Chandrashekhar%20Rao%20(KCR)%20assured%20party%20workers%20in%20Gajwel%20recently%20that%20he%20would%20spend%20at%20least%20one%20day%20a%20month%20in%20his%20constituency%20to%20be%20available%20to%20them.%20Not%20only%20was%20this%20meeting%20unusual%2C%20but%20so%20was%20his%20tone.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGajwel%20has%20been%20KCR%E2%80%99s%20constituency%20since%202014.%20In%20the%20last%20decade%20as%20Gajwel%20MLA%2C%20he%20has%20hardly%20ever%20addressed%20a%20party%20workers%E2%80%99%20meeting%20in%20the%20constituency%20and%20has%20never%20taken%20it%20upon%20himself%20to%20appeal%20to%20voters%20to%20support%20his%20candidature.%20As%20an%20unchallenged%20leader%20in%20Telangana%2C%20his%20victory%20in%20Gajwel%20seemed%20%3Cem%3Efait%20accompli%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20311px)%2085vw%2C%20311px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22311%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-300x248.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-1024x845.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681756%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22256%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20doubts%20are%20being%20cast%20in%20political%20circles%20this%20time%20around%20on%20his%20perceived%20invincibility%20in%20Gajwel%20following%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20contest%20another%20constituency%2C%20Kamareddy%2C%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Assembly%20elections.%20Opposition%20parties%20say%20KCR%20is%20%E2%80%9Cfleeing%20to%20Kamareddy%E2%80%9D%20in%20search%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Csafe%20seat%E2%80%9D%20as%20he%20is%20doubtful%20of%20his%20victory%20in%20Gajwel.%20They%20say%20it%20is%20also%20indicative%20of%20the%20political%20mood%20against%20BRS%2C%20across%20the%20119%20constituencies%20in%20the%20state%2C%20which%20will%20go%20to%20polls%20on%20November%2030.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20contest%20may%20not%20be%20as%20easy%20as%20KCR%20and%20BRS%20would%20have%20expected%20to%20be%20in%20Kamareddy%2C%20as%20Congress%20chief%20Revanth%20Reddy%20has%20decided%2C%20only%20this%20week%2C%20to%20throw%20his%20hat%20in%20the%20ring.%20In%20Gajwel%2C%20KCR%20will%20clash%20with%20his%20friend-turned-foe%20Eatala%20Rajender%20(BJP)%2C%20who%20has%20vowed%20to%20%E2%80%9Cteach%20KCR%20a%20lesson%E2%80%9D%20in%20his%20own%20backyard.%20For%20the%20BRS%20chief%2C%20a%20defeat%20in%20any%20of%20these%20seats%20or%20worse%2C%20both%2C%20could%20be%20a%20major%20embarrassment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-polls-brs-kcr-congress-bjp%5C%22%3ETelangana%20Polls%3A%20BRS%20Has%20Reason%20Not%20To%20Be%20Overconfident%20With%20Congress%20Poised%20To%20Challenge%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20interesting%20to%20note%20that%20Gajwel%20and%20Kamareddy%20are%20not%20the%20home%20constituencies%20of%20Rajender%20and%20Reddy.%20Both%20Rajender%20and%20Reddy%20want%20to%20settle%20personal%20scores%20with%20KCR%20in%20a%20direct%20contest.%20Rajendar%2C%20as%20always%2C%20will%20also%20contest%20from%20his%20traditional%20seat%20of%20Huzurabad%2C%20where%20is%20the%20incumbent.%20Reddy%20will%20also%20run%20for%20election%20from%20the%20Kodangal%20assembly%20segment%2C%20as%20he%20has%20been%20doing%20since%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGajwel%3A%20A%20clash%20against%20former%20confidant%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUntil%202004%2C%20KCR%E2%80%99s%20borough%20was%20Siddipet%2C%20which%20he%20represented%20for%20nearly%20two%20decades.%20Between%202004%20and%202014%2C%20he%20served%20as%20an%20MP.%20In%202014%2C%20riding%20high%20on%20Telangana%20sentiment%2C%20KCR%20emerged%20victorious%20from%20Gajwel%2C%20by%20defeating%20the%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20(TDP)%E2%80%99s%20Pratap%20Reddy%20Vanteru%20by%2019%2C391%20votes%20%5Bhis%20nephew%20T.%20Harish%20Rao%20was%20elected%20to%20the%20Siddipet%20constituency%20after%20KCR%20vacated%20it%20in%202004%5D.%20The%20seat%20had%20until%20then%20alternated%20between%20Congress%20and%20TDP.%20Since%202014%2C%20Gajwel%20has%20assumed%20the%20status%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9CVIP%20constituency%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20as%20expected%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20carried%20out%20a%20slew%20of%20development%20activities.%20According%20to%20BRS%2C%20Gajwel%20under%20KCR%20has%20seen%20unprecedented%20development%2C%20making%20it%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmodel%20constituency%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKCR%20clashed%20with%20the%20same%20Pratap%20Reddy%20in%20the%202018%20assembly%20elections%2C%20who%20had%20by%20then%20shifted%20to%20the%20Congress%20party.%20The%20chief%20minister%20polled%201%2C25%2C444%20votes%2C%20compared%20to%20Pratap%20Reddy%E2%80%99s%2067%2C154%20%E2%80%93%20helping%20the%20former%20secure%20a%20huge%20majority%20of%20around%2058%2C000%20votes.%20In%20the%20aftermath%20of%20his%202018%20loss%2C%20Pratap%20Reddy%20shifted%20his%20allegiance%20to%20BRS%20and%20was%20made%20the%20chairman%20of%20Telangana%20Forest%20Development%20Corporation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20strong%20candidate%20like%20Pratap%20Reddy%20out%20of%20the%20fray%2C%20Gajwel%20should%20have%20ideally%20been%20a%20cakewalk%20for%20KCR.%20However%2C%20that%20was%20not%20to%20be%2C%20with%20KCR%E2%80%99s%20b%C3%AAte%20noire%2C%20Rajender%2C%20raring%20to%20shock%20his%20former%20boss.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERajender%20as%20the%20BJP%20candidate%20had%20defeated%20BRS%20(then%20Telangana%20Rashtra%20Samithi)%20in%20a%20high-stakes%20battle%20in%20Huzurabad%20in%202021%2C%20following%20his%20unceremonious%20exit%20from%20KCR%E2%80%99s%20cabinet%20and%20party.%20It%20was%20alleged%20at%20that%20time%20that%20KCR%20had%20used%20all%20his%20might%20to%20see%20Rajender%20defeated%2C%20by%20pumping%20in%20huge%20sums%20of%20money%20and%20using%20official%20machinery.%20A%20posse%20of%20top-rung%20TRS%20leaders%20and%20cabinet%20ministers%20had%20descended%20on%20Huzurabad.%20However%2C%20Rajender%20emerged%20victorious%20with%20a%20winning%20margin%20of%20over%2023%2C000%20votes%2C%20earning%20him%20a%20place%20and%20respect%20not%20just%20in%20his%20new%20party%2C%20the%20BJP%2C%20but%20also%20in%20the%20anti-KCR%20camp.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02134947%2FF9sj02TbYAAwVbW.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02134947%2FF9sj02TbYAAwVbW.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02134947%2FF9sj02TbYAAwVbW-300x200.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-683125%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EEatala%20Rajender%20with%20his%20supporters.%20Photo%3A%20X%20(Twitter)%2F%40Eatala_Rajender%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ERajender%E2%80%99s%20bid%20from%20Gajwel%20has%20not%20only%20enthused%20the%20BJP%20cadre%20and%20leadership%20but%20also%20has%20been%20drawing%20support%20from%20other%20parties%20and%20civil%20society%20groups%20opposed%20to%20KCR%20and%20BRS.%20As%20someone%20who%20had%20been%20associated%20with%20the%20TRS%20and%20Telangana%20movement%20for%20over%2020%20years%2C%20and%20later%20as%20finance%20minister%20and%20health%20minister%20in%20the%20KCR%20government%2C%20Rajender%20is%20a%20popular%20face%20and%20is%20known%20to%20have%20good%20connections%20across%20the%20state.%20The%20disgruntled%20BRS%20workers%20and%20leaders%20in%20Gajwel%20have%20also%20thrown%20their%20weight%20behind%20him.%20He%20has%20traversed%20the%20full%20ideological%20spectrum%2C%20starting%20as%20a%20member%20of%20the%20leftist%20Progressive%20Democratic%20Students%20Union%20in%20his%20youth%20to%20TRS%20(BRS)%20and%20now%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-why-the-huzurabad-by-poll-is-crucial-for-opposition-parties%5C%22%3ETelangana%3A%20Why%20the%20Huzurabad%20By-Poll%20Is%20Crucial%20for%20Opposition%20Parties%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%20could%20also%20work%20in%20Rajender%E2%80%99s%20favour%20is%20the%20perceived%20feeling%20of%20injustice%20by%20his%20Mudiraj%20community%2C%20which%20is%20categorised%20under%20the%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs%20or%20BCs)%20in%20the%20state.%20Rajender%20is%20a%20powerful%20leader%20not%20only%20in%20his%20community%20but%20also%20among%20BCs%20in%20the%20state.%20Since%20his%20sacking%20from%20KCR%E2%80%99s%20cabinet%20in%20May%202021%2C%20Rajender%20has%20been%20mobilising%20BCs%20against%20KCR%20and%20his%20family%2C%20and%20has%20largely%20been%20successful%20in%20characterising%20his%20expulsion%20from%20KCR%E2%80%99s%20cabinet%20as%20an%20%E2%80%9Cinsult%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20BCs.%20Lately%2C%20the%20BRS%E2%80%99s%20decision%20not%20to%20field%20even%20a%20single%20Mudiraj%20in%20any%20of%20the%20119%20assembly%20segments%20has%20also%20angered%20the%20community.%20According%20to%20various%20unofficial%20estimates%2C%20the%20community%20accounts%20for%2012%25%20of%20the%20state%20population%2C%20and%20in%20Gajwel%2C%20they%20are%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fhyderabad%2Featala-pins-hope-on-bc-votes-in-gajwel-showdown%2Farticleshow%2F104637869.cms%5C%22%3Esizeable%20voting%20bloc%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20Mudiraj%20community%20and%20other%20BC%20groups%20in%20Gajwel%20have%20already%20announced%20their%20full%20support%20to%20Rajender.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVoters%20from%20around%20seven%20villages%20in%20Gajwel%2C%20whose%20lands%20were%20affected%20by%20the%20Mallannasagar%20reservoir%2C%20which%20is%20part%20of%20the%20famed%20Kaleshwaram%20Lift%20Irrigation%20Scheme%2C%20have%20been%20livid%20with%20KCR%20over%20inadequate%20compensation%20and%20apparent%20unfulfillment%20of%20promises.%20They%20have%20been%20staging%20continuous%20protests%2C%20demanding%20the%20allotment%20of%20agricultural%20lands%20and%20residential%20plots%2C%20in%20lieu%20of%20what%20they%20had%20lost%20due%20to%20the%20irrigation%20project.%20Rajendar%20is%20hopeful%20of%20securing%20en%20bloc%20the%20votes%20of%20oustees%20of%20the%20irrigation%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20that%20the%20Gajwel%20constituency%20is%20located%20adjacent%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-by-poll-dubbak-bjp-win%5C%22%3EDubbak%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20the%20BJP%20had%20secured%20a%20surprise%20victory%20in%20a%20closely%20contested%20by-poll%20in%202020%20could%20also%20go%20in%20Rajender%E2%80%99s%20favour.%20While%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Raghunandan%20Rao%20had%20polled%2013.75%25%20vote%20share%20(22%2C595%20votes)%20in%20the%202018%20Assembly%20elections%20to%20take%20third%20place%20against%20BRS%E2%80%99s%20winning%20candidate%20Solipeta%20Ramalinga%20Reddy%2C%20Rao%20managed%20to%20secure%2038.47%25%20vote%20share%20(63%2C%20352%20votes)%20in%20the%20by-poll%2C%20held%20mere%20two%20years%20later.%20What%20made%20the%20win%20even%20more%20significant%20was%20that%20Rao%20won%20against%20Reddy%E2%80%99s%20widow%2C%20even%20though%20the%20%E2%80%98sympathy%20vote%E2%80%99%20after%20a%20sitting%20MLA%E2%80%99s%20death%20usually%20sees%20their%20family%20members%20sail%20to%20victory.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20allegation%20against%20KCR%20has%20been%20that%20he%20is%20inaccessible%20to%20party%20workers%20and%20the%20people%20of%20Gajwel%20even%20though%20he%20spends%20considerable%20time%20at%20his%20farmhouse%20in%20the%20constituency.%20His%20nephew%2C%20Harish%20Rao%2C%20is%20said%20to%20handle%20most%20of%20the%20party%20work%20and%20development%20activity%20in%20Gajwel%2C%20on%20his%20uncle%E2%80%99s%20behalf.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F04204057%2Fkcr-harish.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F04204057%2Fkcr-harish.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F04204057%2Fkcr-harish-300x196.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F04204057%2Fkcr-harish-1024x670.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-425082%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22785%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EKCR%20with%20his%20nephew%20T.%20Harish%20Rao.%20Photo%3A%20Facebook%2FT.%20Harish%20Rao%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20KCR%20himself%20pointed%20to%20this%20indirectly%20when%20he%20spoke%20to%20party%20workers%20in%20Gajwel%20in%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fstates%2Ftelangana%2F2023%2Foct%2F21%2Fwill-retain-gajwel-have-reason-to-contest-from-kamareddy-k-chandrasekhar-rao-2625882.html%5C%22%3Erare%20meeting%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20held%20recently%20in%20Gajwel.%20The%20chief%20minister%20said%20the%20people%20of%20Gajwel%20were%20justified%20in%20wanting%20their%20MLA%20to%20be%20available%20to%20them%2