%20finding%20the%20cure.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EL.G.%20Qadri%2C%20played%20by%20Ashutosh%20Gowariker%2C%20in%20a%20theatrical%20speech%20introduces%20%E2%80%98the%20trolley%20problem%E2%80%99%20upon%20which%20the%20moral%20dilemma%20of%20the%20show%20hinges.%20This%20philosophical%20experiment%20asks%3A%20if%20one%20had%20a%20choice%2C%20should%20they%20allow%20a%20train%20to%20run%20on%20its%20track%20and%20kill%20five%20people%20working%20ahead%2C%20or%20should%20they%20flip%20the%20switch%20so%20that%20the%20train%20changes%20its%20track%20and%20kills%20one%20innocent%20person%20instead%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fkaala-paani-is-a-well-mounted-thriller-that-doesnt-trust-itself-enough-to-forgo-the-melodrama%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Kaala%20Paani%E2%80%99%20Is%20a%20Well%20Mounted%20Thriller%20That%20Doesn%E2%80%99t%20Trust%20Itself%20Enough%20To%20Forgo%20the%20Melodrama%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20becomes%20the%20potent%20tool%20with%20which%20every%20cruel%20bureaucratic%20choice%20is%20justified%2C%20to%20the%20extent%20that%20even%20the%20genocide%20of%20tribal%20communities%20is%20proposed%20and%20considered%20as%20the%20difficult%20but%20righteous%20option%20towards%20the%20climax%20of%20the%20show.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20a%20local%20taxi%20driver%20named%20Chiranjeevi%20(played%20by%20Sukant%20Goel)%20who%20was%20a%20sceptic%20of%20tribal%20welfare%20activism%20and%20the%20environment%2C%20finally%20becomes%20a%20devoted%20protector%20of%20the%20tribal%20community%20after%20discovering%20a%20deeper%20connection.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20show%20also%20features%20a%20corrupt%20police%20officer%2C%20played%20with%20mirth%20and%20humour%20by%20Amey%20Wagh%2C%20who%20colludes%20with%20corporate%20overlords%20to%20escape%20the%20islands.%20Throughout%20the%20series%2C%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20corporation%20points%20towards%20a%20sinister%20cause%20behind%20the%20disease%2C%20but%20it%20remains%20a%20cliffhanger%20till%20the%20very%20end.%20As%20the%20characters%20develop%20throughout%20the%20show%2C%20their%20concerns%20and%20interests%20also%20change%20and%20influence%20the%20final%20outcome.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20makers%20of%20the%20show%20also%20refrain%20from%20assuming%20the%20voice%20of%20the%20tribal%20community%20while%20trying%20to%20make%20them%20play%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20determining%20the%20fate%20of%20the%20island.%20However%2C%20the%20lack%20of%20characterisation%20just%20to%20avoid%20appropriation%20feels%20too%20cautious%20and%20unsatisfactory%20at%20times.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20show%20does%20not%20relent%20to%20the%20traditional%20structure%20of%20valorising%20and%20celebrating%20certain%20protagonists%20as%20being%20the%20saviours%20while%20sidelining%20loss%20and%20suffering.%20Rather%2C%20it%20uses%20the%20crisis%20caused%20by%20an%20epidemic%20to%20draw%20parallels%20with%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20the%20characters%E2%80%99%20actions%20and%20not%20the%20characters%20themselves%20that%20serve%20as%20the%20antagonists%20and%20protagonists%20of%20the%20show.%20The%20show%20builds%20up%20an%20emotional%20trajectory%20in%20each%20of%20its%20characters%E2%80%99%20storylines%20that%20moves%20the%20audience%20and%20demands%20a%20few%20teary%20eyes%20quite%20often.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EKaala%20Paani%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Estays%20committed%20to%20depicting%20human%20tragedy%20and%20even%20though%20season%20one%20ends%20with%20the%20promise%20of%20a%20cure%2C%20the%20cathartic%20release%20of%20a%20tragedy%20is%20what%20the%20audience%20carries%20with%20them%20and%20finds%20comfort%20in%20through%20a%20collective%20act%20of