lated%20on%20chat%20groups%20among%20armed%20Israeli%20settlers%20calling%20for%20their%20murder.%E2%80%9D%20El-Rifae%20said.%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6%20In%20response%20to%20this%20disaster%2C%20we%20are%20holding%20this%20event%20as%20an%20urgent%20intervention%20by%20writers%2C%20scholars%20and%20poets%20who%20have%20worked%20at%20the%20unavoidable%20intersection%20of%20art%20and%20politics%20%E2%80%94%20who%20have%20thought%20deeply%20about%20land%2C%20segregation%2C%20colonisation%2C%20history%20and%20liberation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECivil%20rights%20lawyer%20and%20author%20Michelle%20Alexander%20introduced%20the%20evening%2C%20acknowledging%20that%20in%201967%2C%20Dr.%20Martin%20Luther%20King%20Jr.%20was%20scheduled%20to%20give%20his%20speech%20condemning%20the%20Vietnam%20War%20in%20Jane%E2%80%99s%20Chapel%20as%20well.%20The%20speech%20was%20ultimately%20relocated%20to%20Riverside%20Church%2C%20but%20the%20parallels%20remained.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlexander%20quoted%20from%20King%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20come%20to%20this%20magnificent%20house%20of%20worship%20tonight%20because%20my%20conscience%20leaves%20me%20no%20other%20choice.%20A%20time%20comes%20when%20silence%20is%20betrayal.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKing%E2%80%99s%20speech%20set%20the%20stage%20for%20the%20event%E2%80%99s%20theme%20of%20breaking%20silence%20for%20the%20aim%20of%20liberation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20conversation%20moderated%20by%20Alexander%2C%20Khalidi%2C%20professor%20at%20Columbia%20University%20and%20Palestinian-American%20historian%20spoke%20of%20the%20importance%20of%20understanding%20the%20history%20of%20Palestine%20in%20order%20to%20understand%20its%20resistance.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20part%20of%20a%20100-years%20war%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eon%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Palestine%3B%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20a%20war%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Palestine%2C%E2%80%9D%20Khalidi%20said.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20war%20to%20implant%20a%20settler-colonial%20presence%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20an%20indigenous%20people%20which%20is%20being%20pushed%20out%20slowly%20but%20surely.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKhalidi%20was%20joined%20in%20this%20conversation%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EAmerican%20author%20and%20journalist%20Ta-Nehisi%20Coates.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fpalestine-israel-zionism-hindutva%5C%22%3EA%20Prayer%2C%20Chant%20and%20Protest%20Song%3A%20Faith%20Communities%20Must%20Resist%20Their%20Extremists%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECoates%20reflected%20on%20his%20time%20visiting%20Palestine%2C%20where%20he%20said%20he%20felt%20tremendous%20shame%20for%20not%20knowing%20how%20segregated%20the%20land%20was.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20can%20think%20back%20to%20all%20of%20the%20articles%20I%E2%80%99ve%20read%2C%20all%20the%20things%20I%E2%80%99ve%20seen%20said%20about%20how%20complicated%20and%20complex%20the%20situation%20is%20and%20the%20occupation%20is%2C%E2%80%9D%20Coates%20said.%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%98It%E2%80%99s%20complex%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20complicated.%E2%80%99%20And%20it%E2%80%99s%20made%20to%20sound%20as%20if%20you%20need%20a%20degree%20in%20Middle%20Eastern%20studies%20or%20some%20such%2C%20a%20PhD%2C%20to%20really%20understand%20what%E2%80%99s%20happening.%20But%20I%20understood%20the%20first%20day.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20him%2C%20he%20said%20speaking%20up%20is%20personal%20and%20he%20has%20debts%20to%20pay.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20think%20about%20how%20gracious%20people%20were%20when%20I%20was%20over%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20Coates%20said.%20%E2%80%9CI%20think%20about%20how%20they%20took%20me%20into%20their%20homes%2C%20I%20think%20about%20how%20they%20fed%20me%2C%20and%20I%20think%20about%20how%20their%20only%20request%20was%3A%20%E2%80%98When%20you%20go%20back%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20lose%20your%20voice.%E2%80%99%20That%20was%20all%20they%20asked.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlexander%20shifted%20the%20conversation%20to%20the%20political%20realities%20in%20the%20United%20States%20and%20its%20unshakeable%20support%20for%20Israel%2C%20citing%20a%20speech%20delivered%20by%20Joe%20Biden%20in%201986%20where%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20look%20at%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20I%20think%20it%E2%80%99s%20about%20time%20we%20stop%20apologising%20for%20our%20support%20for%20Israel.%20There%E2%80%99s%20no%20apology%20to%20be%20made.%20None.%20It%20is%20the%20best%20%243%20billion%20dollar%20investment%20we%20make.%E2%80%9D%20She%20asked%20Khalidi%20and%20Coates%20what%20people%20needed%20to%20understand%20about%20Biden%E2%80%99s%20statement.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKhalidi%20said%20that%20in%20addition%20to%20political%20strategy%20and%20imperial%20interests%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20understand%20that%20politicians%20are%20%E2%80%9Cbought%20and%20sold%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20like%20politicians%2C%20university%20administrations%20and%20the%20media%20kowtow%20to%20a%20single%20narrative%20because%20of%20money%20and%20power.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20not%20a%20war%20on%20the%20Palestinians%20waged%20by%20the%20Zionist%20movement%20or%20Israel%20alone.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20war%20waged%20on%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20by%20Israel%20and%20the%20United%20States%2C%E2%80%9D%20Khalidi%20said.%20%E2%80%9CThose%20are%20our%20weapons.%20Those%20are%20American%20F-35s%2C%20American%20F-15s.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20continued%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20to%20do%20something%20about%20our%20complicity%20in%20the%20killing%20so%20far%20of%209%2C000%20people%2C%20almost%204%2C000%20of%20them%20children.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECoates%20closed%20off%20the%20conversation%20speaking%20of%20his%20responsibility%20and%20moral%20conscience.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20midst%20of%20bombs%20being%20dropped%20on%20children%2C%20you%20have%20to%20speak%2C%E2%80%9D%20Coates%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20conversation%20was%20followed%20by%20a%20message%20from%20Rabbis%20Brant%20Rosen%20and%20Alissa%20Wise%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisrael-palestine-jewish-voice-for-peace-apartheid%5C%22%3EJewish%20Voice%20for%20Peace%3C%2Fa%3E%20Rabbinical%20Council%2C%20read%20by%20Jewish%20Voice%20for%20Peace%20member%20Morgan%20Bassichis.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20rabbis%20and%20Jewish%20leaders%2C%20we%20join%20you%20in%20your%20despair%2C%20your%20grief%2C%20your%20fear%2C%20your%20fear%2C%20your%20terror%20and%20your%20uncertainty%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20read.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20know%20all%20too%20well%20that%20in%20moments%20of%20intensified%20Israeli%20aggression%2C%20there%20are%20accelerated%20attempts%20by%20those%20who%20fear%20peace%2C%20by%20those%20who%20fear%20freedom%20to%20shut%20down%20voices%20who%20imagine%20a%20new%20world.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReverend%20Raschaad%20Hoggard%20closed%20off%20the%20evening%20by%20circling%20back%20to%20Martin%20Luther%20King%20Jr%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBeyond%20Vietnam%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20speech.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrom%20King%E2%80%99s%20speech%2C%20Hoggard%20read%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20call%20for%20a%20worldwide%20fellowship%20that%20lifts%20neighborly%20concern%20beyond%20one%E2%80%99s%20tribe%2C%20race%2C%20class%20and%20nation%20is%20in%20reality%2C%20a%20call%20for%20all%20embracing%20and%20embracing%20an%20unconditional%20love%20for%20all%20mankind.%20This%20oft-misu