-at-rs-292-cr-misses-estimates-123110200735_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fberger-paints-india-net-profit-rises-33-at-rs-292-cr-misses-estimates-123110200735_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Cost%20Pressures%2C%20Low%20Demand%20Drag%20October%20Manufacturing%20Activity%20to%208-Month%20Low%3A%20PMI%20Survey%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02154629%2Fimage-1467.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20India%E2%80%99s%20manufacturing%20activity%20in%20October%20grew%20at%20the%20slowest%20pace%20in%20eight%20months%2C%20due%20to%20rising%20cost%20pressures%20and%20a%20decline%20in%20demand%20for%20consumer%20goods%2C%20a%20private%20survey%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20happened%20despite%20an%20increase%20in%20new%20orders%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Purchasing%20Managers%E2%80%99%20Index%20(PMI)%20fell%20to%2055.5%20in%20October%20from%2057.5%20in%20September%2C%20the%20latest%20survey%20released%20by%20S%26amp%3BP%20Global%20on%20Wednesday%20(November%202)%20showed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fmanufacturing-pmi-falls-to-an-eight-month-low-11698863671078.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EMint%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20though%20the%20October%20PMI%20Manufacturing%20data%20was%20above%20its%20long-run%20average%20of%2053.9%2C%20it%20was%20the%20slowest%20rate%20of%20expansion%20recorded%20since%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPMI%20values%20are%20reported%20as%20a%20single%20number%20(usually%20on%20a%20scale%20of%200-100)%2C%20where%20values%20above%2050%20typically%20indicate%20expansion%2C%20and%20values%20below%2050%20suggest%20contraction.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20rate%20of%20job%20creation%20was%20the%20slowest%20since%20April%2C%20the%20survey%20noted%2C%20adding%20that%20only%204%25%20of%20companies%20are%20hiring%20additional%20people%20and%2095%25%20are%20not%20hiring%20new%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBusiness%20confidence%20slipped%20to%20a%20five-month%20low%20amid%20concerns%20surrounding%20inflation%20and%20demand%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20survey%E2%80%99s%20new%20orders%20index%20slipped%20to%20a%20one-year%20low%2C%20as%20some%20firms%20raised%20concerns%20about%20the%20current%20demand%20picture%20for%20their%20products.%20Consumer%20goods%20were%20behind%20most%20of%20the%20slowdown%2C%20recording%20considerably%20softer%20increases%20in%20sales%2C%20production%2C%20exports%2C%20input%20inventories%20and%20buying%20levels%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Pollyanna%20De%20Lima%2C%20economics%20associate%20director%20at%20S%26amp%3BP%20Global%20Market%20Intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20saw%20further%20indication%20of%20broadly-stable%20inflationary%20forces%20across%20the%20manufacturing%20industry.%20It%20appears%20that%20a%20moderate%20increase%20in%20input%20costs%20was%20simply%20passed%20on%20to%20clients.%20Nonetheless%2C%20qualitative%20evidence%20from%20the%20future%20output%20question%20revealed%20an%20interesting%20finding%2C%20as%20reports%20of%20rising%20inflation%20expectations%20were%20expected%20to%20dent%20demand%20and%20subsequently%20production%20growth%20over%20the%20coming%2012%20months%2C%E2%80%9D%20added%20De%20Lima.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFinancial%20markets%20pay%20close%20attention%20to%20PMI%20data%2C%20and%20significant%20deviations%20from%20expectations%20can%20influence%20asset%20prices%2C%20including%20stocks%2C%20bonds%2C%20and%20currencies.%20For%20example%2C%20a%20higher-than-expected%20PMI%20can%20boost%20investor%20confidence%2C%20while%20a%20lower-than-expected%20PMI%20can%20lead%20to%20market%20volatility.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698920516000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02154629%2Fimage-1467.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire