20of%20sexual%20harassment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20took%20me%20to%20a%20road%20behind%20the%20Natyaghar%2C%20which%20was%20deserted%20and%20there%20all%20of%20sudden%20he%20broke%20down%20in%20tears%20and%20embraced%20me%20tightly%20even%20before%20I%20could%20react.%20He%20quickly%20started%20running%20his%20hands%20all%20over%20my%20body%20and%20started%20rubbing%20his%20against%20mine%20in%20the%20most%20gross%20manner%20that%20one%20can%20imagine.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20guide%20told%20me%20that%20he%20would%20only%20allow%20me%20to%20submit%20my%20thesis%20if%20I%20met%20him%20alone%20in%20a%20hotel%20room.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20are%20some%20excerpts%20from%20formal%20complaints%20filed%20and%20statements%20made%20by%20students%20at%20Visva-Bharati%20University%20this%20year%20and%20the%20last.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVisva-Bharati%20was%20founded%20by%20Rabindranath%20Tagore%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fvisva-bharati-university-unesco-living-heritage-art-craft%5C%22%3Ewas%20recently%20declared%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20first%20living%20heritage%20university%3C%2Fa%3E.%20For%20suffering%20students%20though%2C%20the%20central%20university%20has%20become%20more%20of%20a%20living%20nightmare%20than%20a%20sanctuary%20of%20learning%20and%20peace.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20PhD%20student%20who%20lodged%20a%20complaint%20against%20a%20senior%20teacher%20in%20the%20department%20of%20education%2C%20Rajarshi%20Roy%2C%20said%20that%20Roy%E2%80%99s%20ties%20to%20senior%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20leaders%20has%20ensured%20for%20him%20a%20degree%20of%20safety%20in%20his%20position.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CRajarshi%20Roy%20is%20my%20PhD%20guide%20and%20a%20powerful%20man.%20He%20is%20related%20to%20an%20influential%20BJP%20MP%20in%20the%20state.%20His%20wife%20is%20a%20BJP%20worker.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20he%20remains%20in%20his%20teaching%20position%2C%20despite%20spending%20days%20in%20jail%20over%20rape%20attempt%20charges.%20Because%20of%20his%20political%20influence%2C%20the%20V-C%20is%20protecting%20him%20instead%20of%20following%20the%20ICC%20recommendations%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20PhD%20student%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERoy%20allegedly%20turned%20down%20the%20student%E2%80%99s%20requests%20for%20pre-PhD%20submission%2C%20extension%2C%20and%20re-registration%2C%20reportedly%20due%20to%20the%20student%E2%80%99s%20refusal%20to%20accept%20his%20alleged%20advances.%20The%20situation%20intensified%20when%20the%20student%20filed%20a%20formal%20complaint%20with%20the%20university%E2%80%99s%20ICC%20in%20June%202022.%20Roy%20pushed%20for%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20the%20complaint%2C%20and%20was%20allegedly%20backed%20by%20another%20faculty%20member%2C%20the%20student%20said.%20With%20no%20response%20from%20the%20authorities%2C%20the%20student%20went%20to%20the%20police%20and%20an%20FIR%20was%20lodged%20against%20the%20guide%20in%20May%2C%2011%20months%20after%20her%20initial%20complaint%20to%20the%20ICC.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3E%20The%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20seen%20her%20police%20complaint%2C%20which%20was%20turned%20into%20an%20FIR%2C%20and%20the%20ICC%20complaint%20she%20filed.%20Multiple%20emails%20she%20sent%20Roy%2C%20requesting%20him%20to%20check%20her%20PhD%20work%2C%20were%20also%20seen.%20This%20student%2C%20like%20others%2C%20requested%20anonymity%20for%20this%20piece.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnly%2048%20minutes%20after%20she%20filed%20the%20police%20complaint%2C%20Sakuntala%20Misra%2C%20the%20chairperson%20of%20the%20ICC%2C%20sent%20out%20the%20report%20that%20had%20actually%20found%20Rajarshi%20Roy%20guilty%20three%20months%20prior%2C%20back%20in%20February%202023.%20Roy%20was%20notably%20implicated%20twice%20in%202016%20and%202019%2C%20in%20cases%20that%20had%20to%20do%20with%20sexual%20harassment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ICC%20report%20concluded%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20established%20and%20confirmed%20that%20the%20respondent%20(Rajarshi%20Roy)%20is%20found%20guilty%20of%20repeated%20offence%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20of%20lady%20as%20per%20provisions%20of%20Section%202(n)%20(i)%2C%20(ii)%2C%20(iii)%20%26amp%3B%20(v)%20of%20the%20Sexual%20Harassment%20of%20Women%20at%20Workplace%20(Prevention%2C%20Prohibition%20and%20Redressal)%20Act%2C%202013%20and%20clause%20D%20(1)%20(i)%2C%20(ii)%2C%20(iii)%20%26amp%3B%20(v)%20of%20the%20Policy%20on%20Prevention%20of%20Sexual%20Harassment%20of%20Women%20at%20Workplace%20(PSHWW)%20of%20Visva-Bharati.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERajarshi%20Roy%20was%20arrested%20and%20later%20released%20on%20bail.%20Subsequently%2C%20he%20faced%20a%20month-long%20suspension%20from%20the%20University%2C%20but%20has%20since%20returned%20to%20work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERoy%E2%80%99s%20phone%20is%20switched%20off%20and%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20reach%20him%20otherwise.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20submitted%20our%20report%20to%20the%20university%20authorities.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20anything%20more%20to%20say%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sakuntala%20Misra%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20faculty%20member%2C%20assistant%20professor%20of%20dance%2C%20Sumit%20Basu%2C%20who%20was%20detained%20for%20around%20two%20weeks%20in%20April%202022%20for%20allegedly%20hurling%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fkolkata-news%2Fvisva-bharati-asst-professor-arrested-for-alleged-casteist-slur-against-student-101649685687854.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecastiest%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20abuses%20at%20a%20Dalit%20student.%20However%2C%20Visva-Bharati%20chose%20to%20enforce%20only%20a%20weeklong%20suspension%2C%20which%20went%20against%20the%20established%20rules%20and%20guidelines.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPrashanta%20Ghosh%2C%20a%20faculty%20member%20in%20the%20department%20of%20music%20at%20Sangeet%20Bhavan%2C%20did%20not%20experience%20any%20repercussions%20despite%20facing%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20in%202023.In%20July%202023%2C%20the%20student%20filed%20a%20police%20complaint%2C%20accusing%20Ghosh%20of%20attempted%20molestation.%20In%20the%20police%20complaint%2C%20turned%20into%20an%20FIR%2C%20submitted%20by%20another%20research%20scholar%2C%20it%20she%20reported%20that%20Ghosh%20had%20allegedly%20harassed%20and%20stalked%20her%20over%20an%20extended%20period%2C%20even%20sharing%20pornography%20with%20her%20against%20her%20consent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20obtained%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20FIR%20where%20she%20stated%20that%20the%20teacher%20threatened%20to%20ruin%20her%20career%20if%20she%20did%20not%20comply%20with%20his%20requests%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20made%20it%20clear%20in%20no%20uncertain%20terms%20that%20I%20need%20to%20maintain%20a%20physical%20relationship%20with%20him%20and%20while%20maintaining%20such%20relationship%20I%20should%20mimic%20the%20actions%20of%20the%20actress%2C%20as%20depicted%20in%20the%20said%20pornographic%20clip.%20He%20kept%20a%20vice-like%20grip%20on%20me%20by%20misusing%20his%20position%20of%20authority%20over%20me%20and%20repeatedly%20threatened%20to%20ruin%20my%20career%20including%20threats%20to%20make%20my%20exam%20papers%20disappear.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EProfessor%20Arnab%20Ghosh%20from%20the%20Department%20of%20Anthropology%20also%20faces%20several%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20since%202021%2C%20as%20well%20as%20charges%20of%20caste%20and%20gender%20discrimination.%20One%20research%20scholar%20has%20said%20that%20she%20was%20refused%20maternity%20leave%2C%20while%20another%20has%20alleged%20she%20was%20called%20a%20%E2%80%9Cbeggar%E2%80%9D%20for%20requesting%20a%20fellowship%20grant.%20Several%20students%20also%20reported%20instances%20where%20Ghosh%20allegedly%20tied%20the%20progress%20of%20their%20theses%20to%20their%20willingness%20to%20%E2%80%9Cmeet%20him%20in%20a%20hotel.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20rejected%20my%20promotion%20from%20Junior%20Research%20Fellow%20to%20Senior%20Research%20Fellow%20despite%20my%20post-graduation%20with%20distinction%20from%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20most%20prestigious%20research%20institutes.%20On%20multiple%20occasions%2C%20he%20lewdly%20told%20me%20to%20%E2%80%98go%20and%20have%20fun%E2%80%99%20with%20my%20husband%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20one%20of%20the%20complainants%20who%20adds%20that%20she%20lost%20a%20fellowship%20grant%20of%20nearly%20Rs%2012%20lakh%20as%20a%20result.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20member%20of%20Ghosh%E2%80%99s%20family%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20Ghosh%20would%20contact%20this%20writer.%20This%20report%20will%20be%20updated%20when%20he%20does.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20August%2011%20and%2012%2C%20two%20posts%20surfaced%20on%20a%20Facebook%20group%20called%20%E2%80%98VB%20Confessions%E2%80%99.%20Such%20%E2%80%98confessions%E2%80%99%20pages%20are%20common%20for%20educational%20institutions%20and%20offer%20students%20anonymity%20when%20they%20write%20it.%20In%20the%20posts%2C%20students%20asserted%20that%20they%20were%20%E2%80%9Cphysically%20and%20mentally%20tortured%20by%20multiple%20teachers%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20music%20department.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EInstead%20of%20investigating%20these%20claims%2C%20the%20university%20dismissed%20the%20allegations%20outright%2C%20labelling%20them%20as%20a%20malicious%20campaign%20against%20an%20internationally%20reputed%20institution.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EV%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eice-Chancellor%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fkolkata-news%2Fvisva-bharati-university-social-media-post-alleges-student-sexually-harassed-101692109847401.html%5C%22%3EBidyut%20Chakrabarty%20staged%20a%20nine-hour%20hunger%20strike%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20campus%20in%20protest%20against%20these%20posts.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELetters%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20students%20have%20made%20multiple%20attempts%20to%20have%20their%20concerns%20addressed.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20ICC%2C%20they%20have%20sent%20several%20letters%20to%20the%20PMO%2C%20the%20President%20of%20India%2C%20the%20National%20Commission%20for%20Women%2C%20the%20Human%20Rights%20Commission%2C%20the%20National%20Commission%20for%20OBC%2C%20the%20University%20Grants%20Commission%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Education%2C%20and%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Women%20and%20Child%20Development.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02141049%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-02-at-11.09.41-AM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02141049%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-02-at-11.09.41-AM.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02141049%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-02-at-11.09.41-AM-300x133.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02141049%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-11-02-at-11.09.41-AM-1024x452.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-683143%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22530%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EOne%20of%20the%20emails%20sent%20by%20students%20to%20the%20PMO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20these%20appeals%2C%20the%20Vice-Chancellor%2C%20known%20for%20frequently%20making%20controversial%20statements%2C%20has%20not%20taken%20significant%20action%20to%20address%20these%20grave%20allegations.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20University%20and%20Mahua%20Banerjee%2C%20in%20charge%20of%20public%20relations%20there%2C%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20decide%20as%20per%20due%20processes%20applicable%20to%20all%20who%20are%20associated%20with%20the%20university.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EProfessor%20Sudipta%20Bhattacharya%2C%20president%20of%20the%20Visva-Bharati%20University%20Faculty%20Association%20and%20a%20faculty%20member%20in%20the%20department%20of%20economics%20and%20politics%20at%20Vidya%20Bhavana%20said%20that%20he%20was%20recently%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fpolitical-vendetta-alleged-in-suspension-of-visva-bharati-professor%5C%22%3Eserved%20with%20a%20chargesheet%20for%20filing%20an%20FIR%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20the%20VC%20for%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fenglish.jagran.com%2Findia%2Fvisvabharati-vc-booked-for-allegedly-insulting-bengalis-on-universitys-website-in-west-bengals-birbhum-10097894%5C%22%3Eallegedly%20anti-Bengali%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%20written%20by%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CProfessor%20Bidyut%20Chakrabarty%E2%80%99s%20inaction%20clearly%20indicates%20an%20intention%20to%20protect%20the%20accused%20faculty%20members%20and%20perpetuates%20an%20environment%20conducive%20to%20sexual%20harassment%20at%20Visva-Bharati%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bhattacharya%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20those%20unhappy%20with%20Chakrabarty%20pointed%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20in%202007%2C%20an%20employee%20of%20Gandhi%20Bhawan%20had%20accused%20him%20of%20sexual%20harassment.%20Delhi%20University%20sexual%20harassment%20committee%20found%20him%20guilty%20in%202010.%20Consequently%2C%20he%20was%20asked%20to%20resign%20from%20his%20positions%20as%20the%20director%20of%20Gandhi%20Bhawan%20and%20the%20head%20of%20the%20political%20science%20department.%20He%20was%20also%20debarred%20from%20holding%20any%20administrative%20post%20in%20DU%20for%20a%20period%20of%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%20RTI%20enquiry%20later%20revealed%20that%20the%20committee%20recommended%20that%20%E2%80%9Cwhenever%20such%20persons%20are%20considered%20by%20the%20University%20for%20any%20assignment%2C%20which%20involves%20intensive%20interaction%20with%20female%20colleagues%2F%20subordinates%2C%20their%20past%20conduct%20is%20kept%20in%20mind.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20university%20has%20meanwhile%20seen%20numerous%20show-cause%20and%20suspension%20orders%20issued%20to%20students%20and%20teachers%20since%20Chakrabarty%20assumed%20his%20position%20as%20V-C%20in%20November%202018.%20The%20university%20has%2C%20so%20far%2C%20embroiled%20itself%20in%20more%20than%20100%20judicial%20proceedings%20and%20has%20allegedly%20taken%20up%20fights%20with%20several%20employees%20and%20students.%20Most%20of%20interim%20court%20orders%20have%20been%20against%20the%20university.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAparna%20Bhattacharya%20is%20a%20Kolkata-based%20political%20analyst%20with%20experience%20in%20campaign%20strategy%2C%20communication%20and%20public%20affairs.%20She%20is%20co-founder%20of%20Populytix%2C%20a%20data%20analysis%20and%20market%20research%20firm.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698914147000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F19180125%2Fimage-1-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fvisva-bharati-university-sexual-harassment%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20university%20has%20seen%20numerous%20show-cause%20notices%20and%20suspension%20orders%20issued%20to%20students%20and%20teachers%20since%20controversial%20V-C%20Bidyut%20Chakrabarty%20assumed%20his%20position%20in%20November%202018.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fvisva-bharati-university-sexual-harassment%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Minority%20Edu%20Body%20Asks%204%20States%20to%20Reconsider%20Criteria%20for%20Granting%20Minority%20Tag%20to%20Institutions%26nbsp%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F22133252%2Fivan-aleksic-PDRFeeDniCk-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20National%20Commission%20for%20Minority%20Educational%20Institutions%20(NCMEI)%20has%20opposed%20the%20criteria%20fixed%20by%20four%20southern%20states%20for%20granting%20minority%20status%20to%20educational%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Telangana%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Karnataka%E2%80%99s%20criteria%2C%20an%20educational%20institution%20is%20granted%20minority%20status%20if%20they%20enrol%20between%2025-50%25%20of%20its%20students%20from%20a%20particular%20minority%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENCMEI%20has%20asked%20the%20four%20states%20to%20align%20with%20its%20criteria%20that%20require%20an%20institution%20seeking%20the%20minority%20tag%20to%20have%20admitted%20at%20least%20the%20same%20percentage%20of%20students%20from%20a%20particular%20minority%20community%20that%20matches%20its%20population%20share%20in%20the%20respective%20state%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ETribune%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fedugraph%2Fnational-commission-for-minority-educational-institutions-glare-on-high-ceiling-for-special-status%2Fcid%2F1976979%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20government%E2%80%99s%20policy%2C%20in%20place%20since%202018%2C%20an%20institution%20set%20up%20by%20a%20minority%20community%20needs%20to%20enrol%2050%25%20of%20its%20students%20from%20that%20community.%20This%20figure%20is%2030%25%20in%20Telangana%20and%2025%25%20in%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENCMEI%20member%20Shahid%20Akhter%2C%20in%20a%20meeting%20on%20October%2016%2C%20expressed%20displeasure%20at%20these%20criteria%20citing%20that%20such%20limits%20would%20deny%20minority%20status%20to%20institutions%20and%20discourage%20philanthropists%20from%20setting%20them%20up%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ETribune%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMinority%20communities%20are%20granted%20the%20power%20to%20set%20up%20and%20administer%20educational%20institutions%20to%20advance%20education%20in%20a%20particular%20community%20under%20the%20constitution.%20These%20institutions%20are%20exempted%20from%20implementing%20other%20reservation%20policies%20and%20are%20allowed%20to%20reserve%20up%20to%2050%25%20seats%20for%20students%20of%20a%20particular%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20has%20been%20observed%20that%20institutions%20set%20up%20by%20a%20particular%20community%20mostly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fedugraph%2Fnational-commission-for-minority-educational-institutions-glare-on-high-ceiling-for-special-status%2Fcid%2F1976979%5C%22%3Eenrol%20students%20from%20other%20communities%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20%3Cem%3ETribune%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJose%20Abraham%2C%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20advocate%20who%20has%20represented%20several%20petitioner%20institutions%20in%20the%20NCMEI%2C%20pointed%20out%20why%20that%20is%20the%20case.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20governments%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Karnataka%20are%20saying%20they%20would%20withdraw%20recognition%20to%20a%20school%20if%20it%20does%20not%20meet%20the%20required%20percentage%20of%20enrolment%20of%20children%20from%20the%20respective%20community.%20Imagine%20communities%20like%20Parsis%2C%20Jains%2C%20Christians%2C%20Buddhists%20and%20Sikhs%2C%20whose%20share%20in%20the%20population%20is%20very%20low.%20To%20ensure%2050%25%20enrolment%20from%20any%20one%20of%20these%20communities%20is%20impossible%2C%E2%80%9D%20Abraham%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fedugraph%2Fnational-commission-for-minority-educational-institutions-glare-on-high-ceiling-for-special-status%2Fcid%2F1976979%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20paper.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20NCMEI%20meeting%2C%20the%20officials%20of%20the%20four%20states%20agreed%20to%20reconsider%20their%20criteria%2C%20a%20source%20told%20the%20paper.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698912657000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F22133252%2Fivan-aleksic-PDRFeeDniCk-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fminority-edu-body-asks-4-states-to-reconsider-criteria-for-granting-minority-tag-to-institutions%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According%20to%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Telangana%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Karnataka%E2%80%99s%20criteria%2C%20an%20educational%20institution%20is%20granted%20minority%20status%20if%20they%20enrol%20between%2025-50%25%20of%20its%20students%20from%20a%20particular%20minority%20community.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fminority-edu-body-asks-4-states-to-reconsider-criteria-for-granting-minority-tag-to-institutions%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Magnitude%205.7%20earthquake%20strikes%20central%20Philippines%3A%20USGS%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698911009000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104910327%2Cimgsize-59130.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fmagnitude-5-7-earthquake-strikes-central-philippines-usgs%2Farticleshow%2F104910291.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104910291.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAn%20earthquake%20of%20magnitude%205.7%20struck%20the%20central%20Philippines%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20USGS%20said.%20The%20offshore%20quake%20was%20at%20a%20depth%20of%2019.2%20km%20(12%20miles)%2C%20USGS%20said%2C%20off%20the%20central%20province%20of%20Eastern%20Samar.%20The%20Philippine%20Institute%20of%20Volcanology%20and%20Seismology%20warned%20of%20damage%20and%20aftershocks%20in%20an%20advisory%20but%20there%20were%20no%20immediate%20reports%20of%20casualties.%20The%20Philippines%20lies%20on%20the%20%26quot%3BRing%20of%20Fire%26quot%3B%2C%20a%20belt%20of%20volcanoes%20circling%20the%20Pacific%20Ocean%20that%20is%20prone%20to%20earthquakes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fmagnitude-5-7-earthquake-strikes-central-philippines-usgs%2Farticleshow%2F104910291.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fmagnitude-5-7-earthquake-strikes-central-philippines-usgs%2Famp_articleshow%2F104910291.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fmagnitude-5-7-earthquake-strikes-central-philippines-usgs%2Famp_articleshow%2F104910291.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bihar%20Caste%20Survey%3A%20The%20Who%E2%80%99s%20Who%20in%20the%20Data%20%7C%20Madaria%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02123121%2FBihar-Kosi-River-Story-Photo-Manoj-Singh-text.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBeyond%20politics%2C%20the%20Bihar%20caste%20survey%20is%20a%20revolutionary%20document.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EA%20public%20document%2C%20the%20first%20ever%20after%201931%2C%20allowing%20for%20people%20to%20stand%20up%20and%20be%20counted.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20go%20down%20to%20the%20wire%2C%20on%20what%20each%20of%20the%20numbers%20unveiled%20mean.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWho%20are%20the%20people%20referred%20to%20by%20percentages%20in%20the%20survey%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EToday%20we%20look%20at%20Madaria%20(86%2C658%20people).%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECastes%20were%20not%20created%20in%20the%20heavens.%20Nor%20did%20God%20ask%20humans%20to%20discriminate%20amongst%20themselves.%20There%20is%20no%20dearth%20of%20evidence%20for%20this.%20One%20such%20piece%20of%20evidence%20is%20existence%20of%20the%20Madaria%20people%20%E2%80%93%20a%20caste%20which%20came%20into%20being%20during%20the%20British%20rule%2C%20after%201857.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20isolated%20caste%20is%20present%20only%20in%20the%20border%20districts%20of%20Bihar%20and%20Jharkhand.%20No%20matter%20how%20hard%20you%20try%2C%20you%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20locate%20members%20of%20this%20caste%20anywhere%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETheir%20story%20is%20not%20very%20old%20but%20it%20has%20not%20been%20recorded%20in%20history%20in%20a%20systematic%20manner.%20Ethnographers%20never%20paid%20attention%20to%20them.%20Most%20sociologists%20also%20did%20not%20give%20them%20much%20importance.%20Madarias%20currently%20live%20in%20Sanhaula%20and%20Dhoraiya%20blocks%20of%20two%20districts%20of%20Bihar%20%E2%80%93%20Bhagalpur%20and%20Banka%20respectively.%20But%20who%20are%20they%20and%20what%20earned%20them%20the%20name%20Madaria%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20337px)%2085vw%2C%20337px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22337%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742.jpg%20838w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-210x300.jpg%20210w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-715x1024.jpg%20715w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682410%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22483%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ELet%20us%20first%20find%20out%20about%20their%20traditional%20profession.%20The%20members%20of%20the%20Madaria%20caste%20have%20largely%20been%20engaged%20in%20farming.%20Most%20of%20them%20own%20tiny%20tracts%20of%20land%20where%20they%20grow%20food%20to%20sustain%20them%20for%20three%20to%20six%20months.%20For%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20year%2C%20they%20have%20to%20work%20as%20agricultural%20or%20daily%20wage%20labourers%2C%20building%20and%20painting%20houses%2C%20working%20in%20grocery%20shops%20or%20sorting%20grain%20in%20the%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20point%20one%20might%20be%20wondering%20whether%20they%20are%20Hindu%20or%20Muslim.%20If%20they%20are%20Hindus%2C%20one%20might%20further%20wonder%20if%20they%20are%20a%20so-called%20%E2%80%98untouchable%E2%80%99%20caste.%20I%20would%20not%20be%20surprised%20if%20such%20questions%20come%20to%20your%20mind.%20As%20stated%20above%2C%20castes%20were%20not%20created%20in%20heavens%2C%20and%20it%20was%20on%20the%20earth%20that%20inhabitants%20created%20religions%20and%20castes%20to%20identify%20themselves.%20For%20example%2C%20someone%20who%20rears%20cows%20and%20buffaloes%20is%20a%20Gwala%20or%20Yadav.%20Someone%20who%20makes%20comfortable%20shoes%20and%20other%20items%20from%20leather%20is%20a%20Chamar.%20Someone%20who%20beautifies%20people%20by%20shaving%20hair%20is%20a%20Nayi.%20If%20someone%20makes%20society%20clean%20by%20washing%20the%20dirty%20clothes%20of%20others%2C%20he%20is%20a%20Dhobi%2C%20and%20if%20someone%20cultivates%20paddy%2C%20he%20is%20a%20Dhanuk.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20people%20of%20the%20Madaria%20caste%20are%20basically%20Dhanuks%2C%20and%20categorised%20as%20Madaria%20Muslims%20and%20Dhanuk%20Hindus.%20The%20Dhanuks%20of%20Bihar%20are%20no%20longer%20the%20same%20Dhanuks%20who%20used%20to%20add%20the%20word%20Mandal%20to%20their%20names.%20Now%2C%20they%20consider%20themselves%20equivalent%20to%20the%20Kurmi%20caste%20living%20in%20the%20area%20south%20of%20the%20Ganges.%20It%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20research%20why%20the%20Kurmis%20living%20in%20the%20districts%20like%20Patna%2C%20Nalanda%2C%20Jehanabad%2C%20Gaya%2C%20Nawada%2C%20etc.%20have%20huge%20land%20holdings%2C%20whereas%20in%20the%20region%20where%20the%20Ganga%20crosses%20the%20state%20boundary%2C%20the%20Dhanuks%20have%20smaller%20land%20holdings.%20Could%20there%20be%20a%20connection%20or%20is%20it%20political%20propaganda%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20population%20of%20Dhanuks%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report%20of%20the%20caste-based%20survey%20conducted%20by%20the%20Bihar%20government%2C%20is%202%2C796%2C605.%20One%20can%20observe%20that%20the%20caste%20is%20widely%20spread%20in%20areas%20of%20North%20Bihar.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20total%20population%20of%20Kurmis%20in%20the%20state%20as%20per%20the%20report%20of%20the%20Bihar%20government%20is%203%2C762%2C969.%20If%20one%20adds%20the%20population%20of%20the%20Madaria%20caste%20to%20it%2C%20that%20is%2C%2086%2C665%2C%20the%20total%20is%206%2C646%2C239.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBefore%20analysing%20the%20political%20implications%20of%20the%20data%2C%20one%20may%20ask%20why%20the%20people%20of%20Madaria%20caste%20accepted%20Islam.%20Was%20there%20any%20pressure%20on%20them%3F%20Had%20any%20Muslim%20ruler%20persecuted%20them%20and%20forced%20them%20to%20do%20so%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20already%20mentioned%2C%20this%20caste%20came%20into%20existence%20during%20the%20British%20era%20post%201857.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20there%20was%20no%20fear%20of%20any%20Muslim%20ruler%20in%20the%20region%20of%20Bihar%20inhabited%20by%20the%20people%20of%20this%20caste.%20But%20there%20was%20certainly%20the%20influence%20of%20saints%20or%20%3Cem%3Epeer%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%93%3Cem%3Efakirs%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20impact%20was%20such%20that%20Bhagalpur%2C%20an%20industrial%20city%20situated%20on%20the%20banks%20of%20Ganga%2C%20which%20was%20once%20famous%20for%20silk%20clothes%2C%20is%20named%20after%20a%20Peer%20%E2%80%93%20Bhagalu%20Mian%20%E2%80%93%20whose%20tomb%20stands%20in%20the%20centre%20of%20the%20city%20even%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20when%20the%20Madaria%20people%20accepted%20Islam%2C%20they%20did%20it%20out%20of%20their%20own%20will%20and%20awareness.%20It%20is%20possible%20that%20they%20had%20learned%20from%20the%20saints%20that%20there%20is%20no%20caste%20discrimination%20in%20Islam%2C%20unlike%20Hinduism.%20No%20matter%20which%20caste%20a%20person%20belongs%20to%2C%20no%20one%20discriminates%20against%20anyone.%20In%20the%20mosque%2C%20everyone%20prays%20together%20and%20embraces%20each%20other.%20After%20embracing%20Islam%20one%20also%20does%20not%20have%20to%20take%20a%20dip%20in%20the%20Ganga.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20what%20might%20have%20happened%20with%20the%20Madaria%20people.%20They%20accepted%20Islam%20but%20their%20caste%20stayed%20with%20them%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20This%20is%20why%20they%20kept%20using%20the%20surname%20%E2%80%93%20Mandal.%20Even%20today%2C%20names%20like%20Suleman%20Mandal%2C%20Rahim%20Mandal%20or%20Ashfaq%20Mandal%C2%A0can%20be%20seen%20in%20land%20deeds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20their%20understanding%20of%20Islam%20expanded%20and%20they%20shed%20their%20Hindu%20identity.%20But%20then%20they%20were%20faced%20with%20the%20dilemma%20of%20the%20names%20to%20use.%20They%20could%20neither%20identify%20themselves%20with%20Syed%2C%20Shaikh%20or%20Pathan%20on%20the%20pattern%20of%20Hindu%20upper%20castes%20nor%20were%20they%20like%20the%20Qureshis%20or%20the%20Lalbegis%20or%20Halalkhors.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20they%20would%20have%20opted%20for%20a%20different%20set%20of%20surnames%20for%20themselves.%20If%20they%20faced%20opposition%2C%20the%20next%20generation%20would%20have%20switched%20to%20other%20names.%20Again%2C%20it%20is%20because%20castes%20were%20not%20created%20in%20heavens%20but%20are%20man-made.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20changed%20when%20the%20country%20gained%20independence%20and%20the%20question%20of%20reservation%20arose.%20The%20people%20of%20the%20Madaria%20community%20accepted%20that%20they%20are%20neither%20Dhanuks%20nor%20Ashraf%20Muslims.%20They%20are%20either%20landless%20or%20farmers%20with%20very%20small%20land%20holdings%2C%20whose%20social%20status%20is%20in%20accordance%20with%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20social%20status%20in%20this%20country%20is%20proportional%20to%20the%20rights%20on%20land.%20That%20is%2C%20the%20more%20land%20one%20has%2C%20the%20higher%20one%E2%80%99s%20status.%20If%20the%20Madaria%20people%20have%20smaller%20land%20holdings%2C%20their%20status%20is%20also%20low.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWell%20before%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Mandal%20Commission%20recommendations%2C%20when%20the%20recommendations%20of%20the%20Mungerilal%20Commission%20were%20implemented%20in%20Bihar%20in%201978%2C%20Madaria%20people%20were%20also%20declared%20entitled%20to%20reservation%20and%20they%20were%20placed%20in%20the%20category%20of%20Yadavs%2C%20Kurmi%2C%20Kushwaha-Koeri%20etc.%20This%20continued%20until%20Nitish%20Kumar%20came%20to%20power%20and%20the%20caste%20was%20declared%20an%20extremely%20backward%20class.%20This%20had%20political%20implications%20as%20the%20decision%20was%20taken%20to%20cause%20a%20dent%20in%20the%20support%20base%20of%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20beyond%20politics%2C%20Madarias%20are%20still%20present%20in%20the%20paddy%20fields%20of%20this%20region.%20Now%2C%20the%20people%20of%20this%20caste%20have%20adopted%20other%20professions%20because%20farming%20is%20no%20longer%20as%20profitable.%20In%20addition%2C%20their%20population%20has%20increased%20but%20the%20size%20of%20land%20holdings%20is%20just%20as%20small.%20After%20the%20separation%20of%20Jharkhand%2C%20the%20situation%20became%20even%20more%20difficult.%20Earlier%20the%20caste%20had%20a%20sizeable%20population%2C%20due%20to%20which%20they%20played%20an%20important%20role%20in%20elections.%20They%20are%20still%20quite%20a%20significant%20vote%20bank%20at%20least%20in%20Sanhaula%20of%20Bhagalpur%20and%20Dhoraiya%20of%20Banka%2C%20where%20they%20hold%20an%20influence%20on%20the%20poll%20outcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20Hindi%20by%20Naushin%20Rehman.%20Read%20the%20Hindi%20original%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewirehindi.com%2F260204%2Fbihar-caste-survey-how-madariyas-originated%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cbr%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERead%20part%20one%20of%20the%20series%2C%20on%20the%20Ghasi%20community%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-ghasi%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20part%20two%20on%20the%20Santrash%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-santrash%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20series%20is%20available%20in%20Hindi%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewirehindi.com%2F260200%2Fbihar-caste-survey-who-are-the-santarash%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20in%20Urdu%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewireurdu.com%2Fauthor%2Fnaval-kishor-kumar%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698910802000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02123121%2FBihar-Kosi-River-Story-Photo-Manoj-Singh-text.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcast