%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Kuki%20tribes%20have%20objected%20to%20Manipur%20government%20sending%20more%20police%20commandos%20to%20Moreh%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20had%20gone%20to%20Moreh%20in%20late%20May%2C%20weeks%20after%20the%20ethnic%20violence%20began%20in%20Churachandpur%20and%20spread%20to%20other%20districts.%20The%20KSO%20alleged%20police%20commandos%20have%20been%20torturing%20Moreh%20residents%20after%20the%20killing%20of%20the%20police%20officer%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Kuki%20body%20Indigenous%20Tribal%20Leaders%20Forum%20(ITLF)%20has%20also%20made%20similar%20allegations.%20It%20criticised%20Biren%20Singh%20over%20what%20it%20claimed%20was%20inequality%20on%20treatment%20of%20two%20cases%20of%20cop%20deaths%20-%20one%20was%20Onkhomang%20Haokip%2C%20who%20was%20killed%20in%20September%2C%20and%20the%20other%20is%20yesterday's%20Moreh%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20Haokip's%20death%2C%20the%20ITLF%20said%2C%20%26quot%3B...%20The%20Chief%20Minister's%20Office%20remained%20startlingly%20mute%20on%20social%20media%2C%20and%20no%20immediate%20action%20to%20investigate%20was%20taken.%20Moreover%2C%20a%20meagre%20ex-gratia%20was%20announced...%20The%20brutal%20and%20cowardly%20assault%20on%20officer%20Haokip%20left%20his%20family%20bereft%2C%20yet%20the%20government's%20indifference%20was%20palpable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EManipur%20Government%20Recommends%20UAPA%20Against%20Kuki%20Group%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Manipur%20government%20in%20a%20statement%20after%20an%20emergency%20cabinet%20meeting%20yesterday%20said%20a%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20has%20been%20filed%20against%20an%20organisation%20called%20World%20Kuki-Zo%20Intellectual%20Council%20(WKZIC)%2C%20which%20issued%20a%20statement%20on%20October%2024%20asking%20%26quot%3Bvolunteers%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20community%20to%20take%20up%20arms%20as%20the%20Kuki%20National%20Army%20and%20other%20insurgent%20groups%20cannot%20%26quot%3Bjoin%20the%20war%26quot%3B%20due%20to%20the%20tripartite%20suspension%20of%20operations%20(SoO)%20agreement%20with%20the%20centre%20and%20the%20state%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20least%2025%20Kuki%20insurgent%20groups%20have%20signed%20the%20SoO%20agreement%2C%20under%20which%20they%20have%20to%20stay%20at%20designated%20camps%2C%20and%20keep%20their%20weapons%20in%20locked%20storage%20for%20regular%20joint%20monitoring%20with%20the%20security%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20WKZIC%20in%20a%20statement%20denied%20it%20ever%20published%20any%20statement%20asking%20for%20volunteers%20to%20%26quot%3Bjoin%20the%20war%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20criticised%20the%20government%20for%20what%20it%20called%20falling%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bfake%20statement%26quot%3B%20issued%20by%20unknown%20miscreants%20to%20tarnish%20the%20image%20of%20the%20WKZIC.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698862140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fkpp064q4_manipur_625x300_01_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmob-surrounds-police-station-near-manipur-chief-ministers-office-cops-fire-in-air-4536465%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Manipur%20Police%20fired%20several%20rounds%20in%20the%20air%20today%20to%20disperse%20a%20mob%20that%20surrounded%20a%20police%20station%20near%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20office%20in%20the%20state%20capital%20Imphal.%20Curfew%20has%20been%20reimposed%20in%20the%20city.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmob-surrounds-police-station-near-manipur-chief-ministers-office-cops-fire-in-air-4536465%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20India-Bangladesh%20Rail%20Link%20Will%20Cut%20Short%20Agartala-Kolkata%20Journey%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20his%20Bangladeshi%20counterpart%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20on%20Wednesday%20jointly%20inaugurated%20three%20projects%20via%20virtual%20mode%2C%20including%20a%20key%20rail%20link%20between%20Tripura's%20Nischintapur%20and%20Gangasagar%20in%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20two%20projects%20inaugurated%20by%20PM%20Modi%20and%20his%20Bangladesh%20counterpart%20are%20the%2065-km%20Khulna-Mongla%20Port%20Rail%20Line%20and%20Unit%202%20of%20the%20Maitree%20Super%20Thermal%20Power%20Plant%20in%20Bangladesh's%20Rampal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20cross-border%20rail%20project%20near%20Tripura's%20capital%20Agartala%20and%20Akhaura%20in%20Bangladesh%20is%20expected%20to%20boost%20cross-border%20trade%2C%20and%20significantly%20reduce%20the%20travel%20time%20between%20Agartala%20and%20Kolkata%20via%20Dhaka.%20When%20fully%20completed%2C%20the%20cross-border%20rail%20link%20will%20cut%20the%20travel%20time%20from%20Kolkata%20to%20Agartala%20from%2036%20hours%20to%2012%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20hailed%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20Cross%20Border%20Rail%20Link%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bhistoric%26quot%3B%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20joy%20that%20we%20have%20come%20together%20again%20to%20celebrate%20the%20successful%20cooperation%20between%20India%20and%20Bangladesh.%20Our%20relationship%20is%20touching%20new%20highs.%20Together%2C%20we%20have%20achieved%20in%20the%20last%20nine%20years%20what%20has%20not%20been%20achieved%20in%20decades%2C%26quot%3B%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20projects%20are%20important%20for%20India's%20Look%20East%20Policy%20and%20will%20also%20boost%20connectivity%20to%20the%20northeast%20which%20is%20heavily%20dependent%20on%20the%20narrow%20Chicken's%20Neck%20or%20Siliguri%20Corridor.%20They%20are%20also%20a%20testament%20to%20India's%20commitment%20to%20the%20region%20around%20the%20Bay%20of%20Bengal%20with%20organizations%20like%20the%20Bay%20of%20Bengal%20Initiative%20for%20Multi-Sectoral%20Technical%20and%20Economic%20Cooperation%20(BIMSTEC)%C2%A0which%20has%20its%20secretariat%20in%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cb%3E'First%20Rail%20Link%20Between%20Northeast%2C%20Bangladesh'%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20Agartala-Akhaura%20Rail%20Link%2C%20PM%20Modi%20highlighted%20the%20impact%20of%20these%20projects%2C%20especially%20during%20the%20pandemic%20with%20oxygen%20trains.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20first%20rail%20link%20between%20the%20northeast%20and%20Bangladesh%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20focused%20especially%20on%20infrastructure%2C%20connectivity%20and%20in%20the%20last%20nine%20years%2C%20we%20have%20started%20three%20new%20bus%20services.%20We%20have%20connected%20Dhaka%2C%20Shillong%2C%20Agartala%2C%20Guwahati%20and%20Kolkata.%20In%20the%20last%20nine%20years%2C%20we%20have%20started%20three%20new%20railway%20services.%20From%202020%2C%20we%20started%20container%20and%20parcel%20services%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20last%20nine%20years%20through%20Chittagong%20and%20the%20Mongla%20Port%2C%20we%20have%20connected%20the%20northeastern%20states%20of%20India.%20Our%20connectivity%20initiative%20worked%20as%20a%20lifeline%20during%20the%20Covid%20pandemic%2C%26quot%3B%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20last%20nine%20years%2C%20four%20new%20immigration%20check%20posts%20have%20been%20opened%20on%20the%20India-Bangladesh%20border%20and%20our%20bilateral%20trade%20has%20nearly%20tripled.%20The%20journey%20of%20these%20nine%20years%20has%20made%20us%20reach%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20Agartala%20Akhaura%20Railway%20Link%20and%20it%20is%20a%20historic%20moment%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cb%3E'Firm%20Cooperation%20Between%20Countries'%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3ESheikh%20Hasina%20said%20the%20relationship%20between%20Bangladesh%20and%20India%20is%20anchored%20in%20history%20culture%20language%20and%20both%20countries%20share%20values%20of%20secularism%2C%20democracy%2C%20and%20countless%20other%20commonalities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20Bangladesh%20attaches%20the%20highest%20importance%20to%20its%20relationship%20with%20India%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20connectivity%2C%20trade%2C%20and%20commerce.%20She%20expressed%20gratitude%20to%20the%20government%20of%20India%20for%20its%20significant%20contribution%20to%20these%20sectors%20and%20also%20extended%20Diwali%20greetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20joint%20inauguration%20of%20these%20projects%20manifests%20the%20firm%20friendship%20and%20collaboration%20between%20our%20two%20countries.%20I%20would%20like%20to%20thank%20you%20PM%20Modi%20for%20his%20warm%20hospitality%20during%20my%20visit%20to%20New%20Delhi%20in%20September%202023%20to%20attend%20the%20G20%20Leaders'%20Summit.%20I%20express%20my%20heartfelt%20gratitude%20for%20your%20commitment%20to%20strengthening%20the%20bonds%20of%20friendship%20between%20our%20two%20countries%2C%26quot%3B%20Prime%20Minister%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20like%20to%20thank%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20for%20jointly%20producing%20the%20biopic%20on%20the%20Father%20of%20the%20Nation%20of%20Bangladesh%20Bangabandhu%20'Sheikh%20Mujibur%20Rehman%20-%20Mujib%3A%20The%20Making%20of%20a%20Nation'.%20I%20would%20like%20to%20extend%20my%20deep%20appreciation%20and%20thankfulness%20to%20Shri%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20collaboration%20in%20the%20connectivity%20and%20power%20sector%20stands%20out%20as%20a%20shining%20example%20of%20our%20cooperation%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20at%20the%20inauguration%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20Bangladesh%20ties%20are%20crucial%20for%20India's%20Act%20East%20Policy%20and%20these%20projects%20have%20also%20laid%20the%20groundwork%20for%20more%20cooperation%20and%20opening%20of%