i%20Lanka%20next%20face%20India%2C%20Bangladesh%20and%20New%20Zealand.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20South%20Africa's%20in-form%20opener%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Quinton%20de%20Kock%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1577-quinton-de-kock-playerprofile%5C%22%3EQuinton%20de%20Kock%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Wednesday%20slammed%20his%20fourth%20hundred%20of%20the%20ICC%20World%20Cup%202023%20and%20became%20the%20first%20batter%20from%20his%20country%20to%20cross%20the%20500-run%20mark%20in%20a%20World%20Cup%20edition.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fdjeuh2d_points_625x300_01_November_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20The%2030-year-old%20opener%20achieved%20this%20milestone%20during%20a%20match%20against%20New%20Zealand%20at%20Maharashtra%20Cricket%20Association%20Stadium%20in%20Pune%20where%20he%20slammed%20a%20sublime%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20his%20ton%20against%20the%20Kiwis%2C%20de%20Kock%20also%20equalled%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Kumar%20Sangakkara%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F369-kumar-sangakkara-playerprofile%5C%22%3EKumar%20Sangakkara%3C%2Fa%3E's%20record%20of%20four%20centuries%20in%20a%20single%20edition%20of%20the%20tournament.%20The%20Sri%20Lanka%20batter%20slammed%20four%20tons%20in%20the%202015%20ODI%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndian%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20holds%20the%20top%20spot%20as%20he%20smashed%20five%20centuries%20in%20a%20single%20edition%20of%20the%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDe%20Kock%20also%20matched%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22A