20Magic%20Bus%20India%20Foundation%E2%80%99s%20work%20is%20to%20provide%20vocational%20skills%20training%20to%20Indian%20kids%20to%20ensure%20a%20secure%20future.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Showed%20me%20the%20right%20path%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EVivek%20points%20to%20the%20example%20of%20Prachi%2C%20a%20young%20girl%20who%20had%20previously%20never%20left%20her%20village.%20Last%20year%20she%20travelled%20to%20a%20national%20athletic%20competition%20in%20Ranchi%2C%20Bihar.%20%E2%80%9CHer%20parents%20were%20in%20complete%20shock%20that%20a%20girl%20who%20never%20left%20the%20home%20before%20has%20performed%20in%20this%20kind%20of%20event%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98If%20you%20had%20not%20tried%20with%20our%20child%2C%20she%20would%20never%20have%20reached%20this%20level.%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnother%20girl%20who%20has%20benefitted%20from%20Magic%20Bus%E2%80%99%20interventions%20is%2017-year-old%20Bittu%20Kumari.%20She%20joined%20the%20programme%20in%202017%20as%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330978%2Fkamlesh-atwal-started-nanakmatta-public-school-uttarakhand-holistic-education-for-students%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20Class%208%20student%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20says%20she%20learned%20life%20skills%20through%20volleyball%20and%20kabaddi%20(volleyball%20has%20since%20been%20replaced%20with%20cricket).%20According%20to%20her%2C%20Magic%20Bus%20helped%20her%20make%20the%20optimum%20use%20of%20her%20talent%20as%20a%20kabaddi%20player.%20%E2%80%9CNow%20I%20am%20a%20state-level%20kabaddi%20player%2C%20and%20I%20want%20to%20play%20at%20the%20national%20level%20also%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20I%20had%20not%20found%20Magic%20Bus%2C%20I%20would%20not%20have%20made%20it%20this%20far.%20They%20showed%20me%20the%20right%20path.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20process%2C%20she%20has%20gone%20from%20being%20scared%20to%20speak%20to%20people%20to%20having%20the%20confidence%20to%20speak%20to%20anyone.%20%E2%80%9CMagic%20Bus%20taught%20me%20communication%20skills%2C%20gave%20me%20confidence%2C%20taught%20me%20what%20is%20right%20and%20what%20is%20wrong%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELast%20year%20Magic%20Bus%20appointed%20Bittu%20as%20one%20of%20their%20community%20coordinators.%20While%20her%20ambition%20is%20to%20become%20an%20IPS%20officer%2C%20she%20also%20plans%20to%20play%20kabaddi%20for%20as%20long%20as%20she%20can.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20parents%20give%20me%20full%20support.%20They%20say%2C%20%E2%80%98When%20my%20daughter%20is%20on%20the%20right%20track%2C%20why%20would%20I%20stop%20her%3F%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20Matthew%2C%20these%20stories%20motivate%20him%20further.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20emotional%20aspect%20of%20our%20work%20reminds%20me%20of%20our%20mission%E2%80%99s%20importance%20and%20the%20need%20to%20stay%20rooted%20in%20the%20communities%20we%20serve.%20By%20understanding%20their%20struggles%20and%20empathising%20with%20their%20challenges%2C%20we%20ensure%20our%20programmes%20remain%20relevant%20and%20effective.%20This%20powerful%20motivation%20drives%20our%20commitment%20to%20doing%20right%20by%20them%20and%20striving%20for%20continuous%20improvement.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20contributed%20by%20the%20Magic%20Bus%20India%20Foundation.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20All%20photos%20courtesy%20Magic%20Bus%20India%20Foundation)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698761468000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F8_11zon-1698734921.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D333285%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Using%20sports%20to%20teach%20crucial%20life%20skills%2C%20Magic%20Bus%20Foundation%20India%20is%20playing%20