%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fsustainable-home-1-1698759499-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333366%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIn%20their%20new%20home%2C%20Ramachandrudu%20and%20Bharani%20embrace%20an%20eco-friendly%20lifestyle.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20container%20house%20boasts%20two%20bedrooms%2C%20a%20drawing%20room%2C%20two%20bathrooms%2C%20and%20a%20staircase.%20Also%2C%20they%20opted%20to%20use%20styrofoam%20as%20an%20effective%20insulating%20material%20for%20the%20containers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20Bharani%20has%20also%20made%20a%20shed%20from%20styrofoam.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20first%20crushed%20styrofoam%20and%20mixed%20it%20with%20cement%20to%20make%20bricks.%20If%20the%20red%20brick%20weighs%203.3%20kg%2C%20the%20styrofoam%20one%20would%20weigh%20nearly%202.5%20kg.%20The%20advantage%20of%20using%20such%20bricks%20is%20that%20close%20to%2070%20percent%20of%20the%20brick%20is%20made%20from%20scrap%3B%20this%20saves%20top%20soil%20which%20is%20usually%20exploited%20during%20construction%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%2029-year-old%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20his%20decision%20to%20join%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20initiative%2C%20Bharani%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CYoungsters%20are%20still%20not%20completely%20aware%20of%20the%20nitty-gritty%20of%20sustainable%20living%20and%20mostly%20find%20themselves%20engrossed%20in%20a%20fast-paced%20lifestyle.%20Nonetheless%2C%20everyone%20should%20be%20encouraged%20to%20live%20a%20green%20life.%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20free%20from%20the%20rat%20race%20and%20lead%20a%20sustainable%20lifestyle.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20individuals%20prefer%20eco-friendly%20homes%20to%20lower%20their%20carbon%20footprint%2C%20minimise%20energy%20usage%2C%20cut%20long-term%20costs%2C%20reduce%20waste%2C%20and%20promote%20healthier%20living.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnyone%20can%20construct%20an%20eco-friendly%20home%20by%20first%20understanding%20the%20qualities%20of%20the%20scrap%20material%20used%20for%20construction%2C%20engaging%20in%20collaborative%20brainstorming%20sessions%20with%20skilled%20tradesmen%2C%20and%20cultivating%20a%20diverse%20capacity%20for%20design%20thinking%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%20also%20shares%20that%20they%20are%20planning%20to%20register%20their%20container%20home%20on%20Airbnb.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98We%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20ACs%20or%20coolers%20to%20regulate%20temperature%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mdpi.com%2F2071-1050%2F14%2F21%2F14393%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESustainability%20Considerations%20of%20Green%20Buildings%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%202022%20report%3C%2Fem%3E%20mentions%20that%20sustainable%20buildings%20can%20conserve%2040%20percent%20more%20energy%20compared%20with%20traditional%20buildings%2C%20increasing%20energy%20efficiency%20and%20decreasing%20carbon%20emissions.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20low-carbon%20materials%20in%20green%20buildings%20reduce%20lifecycle%20emissions%20of%20buildings%20by%20up%20to%2030%20percent.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20conserve%20energy%20in%20their%20unique%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F244161%2Fthese-10-eco-friendly-homes-will-inspire-you-to-live-sustainably%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esustainable%20home%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20father-son%20pair%20have%20employed%20an%20innovative%20masonry%20technique%2C%C2%A0the%20%E2%80%98Rat%20Trap%20Bond%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20was%20popularised%20by%20renowned%20architect%20Laurie%20Baker%20for%20passive%20cooling.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnlike%20traditional%20methods%2C%20this%20technique%20involves%20placing%20the%20bricks%20vertically%20rather%20than%20horizontally%2C%20aiding%20in%20temperature%20regulation%20and%20energy%20conservation%20within%20the%20structure.%20It%20creates%20a%20cavity%20in%20the%20walls%20and%20allows%20the%20thickness%20to%20remain%20the%20same%20as%20a%20conventional%20brick%20masonry%20wall.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20cavity%20helps%20cut%20down%20the%20number%20of%20bricks%20and%20mortar%20used%20by%20up%20to%2030%20percent.%20This%20further%20reduces%20carbon%20footprints%20and%20costs%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ramachandrudu.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fsustainable-home-4-1698759671.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20container%20house%20boasts%20two%20bedrooms%2C%20a%20drawing%20room%2C%20two%20bathrooms%2C%20and%20a%20staircase.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fsustainable-home-4-1698759671.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fsustainable-home-4-1698759671-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fsustainable-home-4-1698759671-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fsustainable-home-4-1698759671-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fsustainable-home-4-1698759671-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333374%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20container%20house%20boasts%20two%20bedrooms%2C%20a%20drawing%20room%2C%20two%20bathrooms%2C%20and%20a%20staircase.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EBesides%20being%20a%20treat%20for%20the%20eyes%2C%20the%20walls%20promote%20natural%20light%20and%20ventilation%20in%20the%20house%20as%20cavities%20act%20as%20thermal%20insulators%20providing%20warmth%20in%20winter%20and%20cool%20air%20in%20summer.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20do%20not%20have%20ACs%20or%20air%20coolers.%20During%20summers%2C%20usually%2C%20the%20interior%20temperature%20is%20at%20least%20seven%20degrees%20cooler%20than%20outside%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20with%20pride.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98We%20repurposed%20old%20wood%20for%20%3Cem%3Ehaveli%3C%2Fem%3E-type%20ambience%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20buying%20new%20wooden%20furniture%2C%20Ramachandrudu%20opted%20to%20source%20antique%20wooden%20doors%2C%20planks%2C%20and%20staircases%20from%20demolished%20homes%20within%20the%20city.%20Additionally%2C%20they%20repurposed%20old%20glass%20doors%20from%20restaurant%20refrigerators%20to%20craft%20elegant%20glass%20window%20doors.%20Furthermore%2C%20they%20used%20cycle%20rims%20to%20create%20unique%20window%20frames%20%E2%80%94%20showcasing%20their%20commitment%20to%20sustainability%20and%20resourcefulness%20in%20every%20aspect%20of%20the%20construction%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20reused%20two%20truckloads%20of%20old%20wood%20in%20the%20construction.%20The%20old%20wood%20gives%20a%20typical%20old%20%3Cem%3Ehaveli%3C%2Fem%3E-type%20ambience%20to%20our%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98We%20harvest%20sunlight%20and%20rain%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3ETwo%20years%20ago%2C%20Ramachandrudu%20installed%20an%20off-grid%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F269780%2Fmy-zero-waste-home-saves-70-energy-by-using-the-sun-to-run-appliances%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esolar%20power%20system%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewith%20a%20capacity%20of%20one%20kilowatt%20to%20fulfil%20the%20household%E2%80%99s%20essential%20energy%20requirements.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20the%20fam