%2C%20we%20were%20able%20to%20export%20our%20Jardalu%20mangoes%20and%20earn%20higher%20profits.%20Despite%20having%20a%20GI%20tag%2C%20we%20never%20got%20the%20benefits%20of%20it%20directly.%20These%20mangoes%20and%20Katarni%20rice%20only%20grow%20in%20Bhagalpur%20and%20Munger%20districts.%E2%80%9D%20Paddy%20farmers%20in%20the%20region%20would%20earlier%20sell%20their%20produce%20in%20the%20domestic%20markets%20at%20Rs%2030%20per%20kg.%20The%20formation%20of%20the%20FPO%20under%20Bayer%E2%80%99s%20guidance%20has%20helped%20them%20fetch%20Rs%2055%20and%20above%20per%20kg%20for%20Katarni%20paddy%2C%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20spurred%20farmers%20in%20Bhagalpur%20to%20rekindle%20their%20love%20for%20Katarni%20rice%2C%20a%20variety%20that%20yields%20double%20the%20income%20in%20the%20same%20land%20compared%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F277852%2Fthoosan-edible-plates-spoons-tableware-from-kerala-biodegradable-wheat-rice%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econventional%20rice%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20compared%20to%2015%20mann%20(600%20kg)%20per%20acre%20yield%20of%20other%20rice%20varieties%20earlier%2C%20farmers%20are%20now%20producing%2020%20mann%20(800%20kg)%20of%20Katarni%20rice%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Manish.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFarmers%20learned%20the%20art%20of%20branding%2C%20packaging%2C%20and%20effective%20marketing%20through%20their%20association%20with%20the%20FPO.%20Manish%20thanks%20Bayer%20for%20playing%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20steering%20the%20farmers%20in%20the%20right%20direction%2C%20and%20helping%20them%20forge%20connections.%20The%20FPO%20now%20aims%20to%20sell%2050%20MT%20of%20%3Cem%3Echuda%3C%2Fem%3E%20(flat%20rice)%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20rice%2C%20from%20January%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20future%20holds%20exciting%20possibilities%2C%20including%20the%20production%20of%20%E2%80%98green%20%3Cem%3Epoha%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98%20from%20Ka