3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20demonstrated%20exceptional%20skill%20in%20sports%2C%20and%20were%20soon%20participating%20in%20the%20foundation%E2%80%99s%20in-house%20sports%20competition%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Toofaan%20Games.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20story%20of%20the%20Toofaan%20Games%20began%20in%202019%20when%20Rohini%20Mukherjee%2C%20the%20then%20head%20of%20Nanhi%20Kali%20operations%2C%20thought%20it%20was%20time%20to%20introduce%20the%20girls%20to%20sports.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20fundamental%20life%20skills%20that%20school%20classrooms%20can%E2%80%99t%20teach%20you%20%E2%80%93%20leadership%2C%20teamwork%2C%20facing%20failure%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%20And%20that%20is%20where%20sports%20came%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAround%201%2C90%2C000%20girls%2C%20including%20the%20twin%20sisters%2C%20get%20at%20least%2010%20years%20of%20schooling%20and%20are%20introduced%20to%20sports%20once%20they%20are%20enrolled%20in%20this%20programme.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20the%20Toofaan%20Games%20have%20turned%20into%20an%20annual%20sports%20gathering%20featuring%20four%20events.%20In%20the%20current%20edition%20that%20started%20in%20August%202023%2C%20almost%20all%20of%20the%20girls%20under%20their%20wing%20are%20competing%20right%20from%20the%20village%20level%20all%20the%20way%20to%20the%20nationals%20organised%20by%20the%20trust.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20organisation%20first%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F318867%2Ffirst-woman-indian-footballer-to-play-english-league-she-kicks-academy-underprivileged-girls-aditi-chauhan%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elooked%20to%20introduce%20sports%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20faced%20a%20challenge%20of%20not%20having%20anyone%20on%20the%20staff%20who%20could%20lead%20a%20sports-focused%20initiative.%20Fortunately%2C%20they%20found%20the%20right%20candidate%20in%20Lisa%20Murawsky%2C%20who%20has%20been%20an%20international%20sports%20consultant%