-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Toofaan%20Games%E2%80%99%20and%20the%20opportunities%20it%20brings%20to%20girls%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3ENaandi%20Foundation%2C%20based%20out%20of%20Hyderabad%2C%20is%20an%20organisation%20working%20diligently%20since%20its%20conception%20in%201998%20towards%20the%20eradication%20of%20poverty%20and%20upliftment%20of%20girls%20and%20women%20across%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20four%20events%20of%20the%20Toofaan%20Games%20that%20the%20girls%20participate%20in%20are%20the%2050m%20sprint%2C%20shuttle%20run%2C%20standing%20long%20jump%2C%20and%20endurance%20run.%20These%20four%20events%20were%20selected%20because%20they%20are%20simple%2C%20easy%20to%20conduct%20and%20give%20the%20girls%20an%20opportunity%20to%20demonstrate%20their%20speed%2C%20agility%2C%20lower%20body%20strength%20and%20stamina.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAbout%20130%20girls%20make%20it%20to%20the%20final%20stage%20of%20the%20Toofaan%20Games%20each%20year%20and%20for%20many%20of%20them%2C%20the%20games%20are%20the%20first%20time%20they%20set%20foot%20outside%20their%20villages.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20significant%20point%20to%20emphasise%20here%20is%20that%20the%20initiative%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F101981%2Fuplabdhi-misha-chandola-teach-girls-project-uttarakhand%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eled%20by%20women%20entirely%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20right%20from%20coaching%20to%20the%20results.%20The%20existing%20infrastructure%20at%20Naandi%20%E2%80%94%20under%20the%20Nanhi%20Kali%20programme%20%E2%80%94%20has%20propelled%20the%20movement%20in%20a%20short%20span%20of%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20%E2%80%98Nanhi%20Kali%20after-school%20tuition%20centres%E2%80%99%20are%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F261243%2Fmalnutrition-orphanage-girl-child-hyderabad-women-donation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emanaged%20by%20a%20