ement%2C%20nutrition%20and%20menstrual%20health%20management.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20do%20girls%20do%20in%20%E2%80%98Sports%20For%20Life%E2%80%99%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20four%20years%2C%20%E2%80%98Sports%20for%20Life%E2%80%99%20has%20lived%20up%20to%20both%20its%20name%20and%20objective%20to%20make%20sports%20a%20part%20of%20everyday%20life%20for%20girls%20starting%20from%20the%20age%20of%20six.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnder%20this%20initiative%2C%20one%20weekly%20sports%20class%20is%20delivered%20on%20SportStar.%20And%2C%20from%20August%20each%20year%20to%20the%20following%20January%2C%20there%20is%20a%20Toofaan%20Games%20sweep%20that%20goes%20across%20the%20country%20%E2%80%94%20about%206000%20villages%20in%209%20states%20%E2%80%94%20as%20widely%20spread%20as%20Darjeeling%20in%20the%20north-east%20to%20Bharuch%20in%20the%20west.%20A%20subset%20of%20the%20girls%20also%20participate%20in%20regular%20football%20coaching.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEvery%20young%20girl%20now%20enjoys%20one%20sports%20class%20per%20week%20where%20they%20not%20only%20play%20but%20also%20learn%20about%20body%20movement%2C%20nutrition%20and%20menstrual%20health%20management.%20It%20is%20a%20fun%20programme%20which%20lets%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F64071%2Fvellore-underprivileged-orphans-hope-house-college-education%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eall%20the%20girls%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewillingly%20participate%20in%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInculcating%20sportsmanship%20and%20inclusivity%20while%20playing%20is%20another%20important%20principle%20that%20these%20girls%20are%20taught.%20%E2%80%9CEvery%20girl%20learns%20to%20include%20everyone%20else%2C%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20matter%20if%20they%20are%20good%20or%20bad%20at%20the%20sport%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rohini%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20academics%20programme%20is%20given%20in%20nine%20l